NK014(pha)014:0: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i gzhal med khang gi rnam par
NK014(pha)014:1: bzhag pa gsal ba'i sgron me'i 'grel pa bzhugs so
NK014(pha)014:2: // bla ma dam pa'i zhabs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)014:3: da ni gzhung gi dka' ba'i don rnams cung zad dgrol bar bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:13: pad ra gsum las mi byed pa ni /
NK014(pha)014:15: rdo rje lag chu me ri har //
NK014(pha)014:16: phyogs rnams kun tu khyab par bya //
NK014(pha)014:18: bde 'dus zhi ba rigs brgya'i sgrub thabs slob dpon gyis mdzad pa las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:19: pad phreng me 'od rdo rje'i phreng bas mdzes par bskor /
NK014(pha)014:21: 'o na khor yug gi tshad rdo ra cha phran gnyis sogs byed pa gang zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:22: spyir srung 'khor gyi rwa gur 'di rnams dmigs pa'i
NK014(pha)014:23: dus su ji tsam nus pa bsgom gyi tshad gcig
NK014(pha)014:25: 'on kyang gzugs brnyan bzhengs pa la sogs la de
NK014(pha)014:26: ltar mi rung bas tshad rnam par bzhag pa ni
NK014(pha)014:28: rdo rje lag chu har bcas pa //
NK014(pha)014:29: rta babs phyed dang gsum du bya //
NK014(pha)014:30: zhes gsungs pa'i rta babs phyed dang gsum ni cha
NK014(pha)014:31: phran phyed gsum yin nam snyam du rtogs par mi
NK014(pha)014:32: bya ste / 'di nas rta rkang gi mtha' gcig
NK014(pha)014:33: nas mtha' shos kyi bar rta babs kyi phreng la
NK014(pha)014:35: de'i phyed cha phyed gnyis yin pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:38: cha chen gnyis po de las kyang phyed nang ma phyed du gtubs te /
NK014(pha)014:39: cha chen gcig shos dang bcas pas gsum 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:42: 'di yang tshad de ltar du bgyis so //
NK014(pha)014:43: de yang srung 'khor rgyas pa'i skabs su mtshon cha 'chol ba /
NK014(pha)014:46: khro bcu rol pa rnams yod pa las /
NK014(pha)014:48: zhi ba la mtshon cha dam tshig mdzad par grags pa ltar na /
NK014(pha)014:49: de la'ang gur rim pa mang po yod kyang /
NK014(pha)014:50: bris pa'i dkyil 'khor dang bstun nas srung 'khor la
NK014(pha)014:51: yod pa thams cad bris cha la ma bris kyang
NK014(pha)014:52: chog pa'i rig pas 'dir rdo rje dang me gur
NK014(pha)014:53: gnyis su bsdu bar mdzad do //
NK014(pha)014:54: de ltar na rdo rje sa gzhi dang ra ba sogs med dam snyam na /
NK014(pha)014:57: za ma tog lta bu'i snod dang /
NK014(pha)014:60: 'dir gur zhes pa rdo rje'i sa gzhi ra ba sogs thams cad kyi spyi ming du bya ste /
NK014(pha)014:62: za ma tog zhes pa de'i mthil dang logs dang
NK014(pha)014:63: khebs thams cad kyi spyi ming yin pa las so
NK014(pha)014:64: // so sor dbye ba med pa bzhin no //
NK014(pha)014:65: rdo rje'i ra ba brtsigs lugs ni /
NK014(pha)014:66: 'og gzhi rdo rje'i sa gzhi brdal ba logs cha
NK014(pha)014:67: chung gnyis la rdo rje sngon po gyen lang gi
NK014(pha)014:68: ra ba zlum po gzhal yas khang dang mnyam pa'i
NK014(pha)014:69: steng du rdo rje'i gur bya ba bzhed la /
NK014(pha)014:70: de dag las me dpung mtha' med du 'phro ba ni me'i gur ro //
NK014(pha)014:71: de ltar na'ang bshad rgyud las /
NK014(pha)014:72: thams cad la ni dbang bsgyur phyir //
NK014(pha)014:73: 'jig rten lha chen rnams kyis bskor //
NK014(pha)014:75: phyogs skyong snam bu mi dgos sam zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:77: thams cad la ni dbang bsgyur phyir //
NK014(pha)014:78: 'jig rten zhes pa 'khor ba'i chos rnams kyang bdag nyid du rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:79: phyi rol du ma h+aa de wa la sogs pa'i lha chen po rnams kyis bskor te /
NK014(pha)014:80: rang rang gi mchod yon dang rgyan dang ldan par 'khod pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:81: de bas na rang bzhin kyang 'di ltar bzhugs la /
NK014(pha)014:82: bri yang de kho na ltar ro //
NK014(pha)014:84: lhag pa gnyis thun mong pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:85: zhes lhag pa gzugs brnyan la'ang bri bar gsungs pas snam bu sger pa byas kyang mi 'gal mod /
NK014(pha)014:86: 'on kyang rdo rje'i las rim gyi thig gi skabs su ma gsungs pa'i phyir 'dir ma byas la /
NK014(pha)014:87: de nas bde 'dus kyi dkyil 'khor bya ba'i rim pa las /
NK014(pha)014:88: phyogs skyong snam bu dkar po'i sna tshogs pad+ma /
NK014(pha)014:93: dang po 'jig rten phyogs skyong la //
NK014(pha)014:94: zhes pad ra'i sa la mdzad snang ba bris cha la dgos kyi /
NK014(pha)014:95: slad du pad 'dab ni logs longs can min pas 'god dka' ba'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:97: rdo rje ra ba'i nang khongs kyi //
NK014(pha)014:98: zhes sogs pad+ma'i lte ba'i phyi mtha' 'khor lo'i mu
NK014(pha)014:99: khyud kyis khyab pa de la bkod pa yin no
NK014(pha)014:101: rdo rjer ba'i khor yug gi nang du sna tshogs pad 'dab /
NK014(pha)014:102: de'i lte ba zlum po leb chags can gyi rgya ni /
NK014(pha)014:103: phyogs gcig nas gcig gi bar la cha phran bdun cu rtsa gnyis pa /
NK014(pha)014:106: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo gsal ba las /
NK014(pha)014:109: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo dpag tu med pa zhig bsgom /
NK014(pha)014:111: 'khor lo'i steng du b+h+r+aum zhes sogs gzhal yas khang bskyed par mdzad ces lha rje so gsungs so //
NK014(pha)014:113: ka rgyan gyi phyi mtha' dang mda' yab kyi phyi
NK014(pha)014:114: thig phrad mtshams nas zlum por bskor ba ni lte
NK014(pha)014:115: ba dang de'i mthar cha phran gcig pa'i mu khyud
NK014(pha)014:116: dang pad+ma'i lte ba'i phyi mtha' dang mnyam pa'i phyi'i
NK014(pha)014:117: mu khyud cha phran gcig pa zhig kyang bskor nas
NK014(pha)014:118: / de'i bar cha chen gnyis kyi de la rtsibs bri /
NK014(pha)014:121: shar dkar ba sogs rigs kyis dabye'o //
NK014(pha)014:123: spar khab kyi le'u dgu par /
NK014(pha)014:124: gzhi tshad med pa'i 'khor lo'i steng du 'khor lo lnga ste 'khor lo drug pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:125: zhes pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:127: de ni nang gi gzhi gdan gyi 'khor lo la dgongs pa'i phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:128: de dang mthun pa 'od rim las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:129: tshad med rtsibs bzhi'i 'khor lo la //
NK014(pha)014:130: rtsibs bzhi mu khyud pany+tsara ldan //
NK014(pha)014:132: de bas na gzhi tshad med pa'i 'khor lo yang rnam pa gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK014(pha)014:133: gzhal yas khang spyi'i 'og gzhi ni /
NK014(pha)014:134: bshad rgyud rol pa chen po'i rgyud kyi le'u lnga par /
NK014(pha)014:136: 'og min la sogs rim bzhin char //
NK014(pha)014:137: 'khor lo chen po'i sa gzhi la //
NK014(pha)014:138: khang par gru bzhi rnam par brjid //
NK014(pha)014:140: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i chos don du //
NK014(pha)014:141: 'og gzhi'i dbyibs ni tshad med de //
NK014(pha)014:142: rgya ma chad pa cha le ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:143: zhes pa'i don rtags 'chad pa'i skabs su ye shes lnga dang sbyar ba'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:144: de'i rtags 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi bar sbyar ba'ang 'brel la /
NK014(pha)014:145: phyogs bcu mun sel gyi le'u dang por yang /
NK014(pha)014:146: rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa ma 'dres pa dang rang gsal ba'i steng la'o //
NK014(pha)014:148: le'u dgu pa b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he zhes pas
NK014(pha)014:149: gzhi tshad med pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lo la
NK014(pha)014:150: gnas pa'i gzhal yas khang chen po /
NK014(pha)014:151: zhes sogs gzhal yas khang gi 'og gzhir mdzad pa
NK014(pha)014:152: dang sngar drangs pa'i rgya cha na 'grel gyi lung
NK014(pha)014:153: des kyang de ltar grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:154: bye brag gdan gyi 'og gzhi ni /
NK014(pha)014:155: 'og gzhi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i gdan zhes sngon gyi mkhan po rnams gsungs te /
NK014(pha)014:156: gzhal yas khang gi nang gi 'khor lo'o //
NK014(pha)014:157: yang rje sgrol ma la sogs pa phal che ba ni /
NK014(pha)014:158: dkyil 'khor spyi dang bstun te 'og gzhi sna tshogs rdo rjer mdzad pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:159: de'i 'thad pa la bla ma 'ga' zhig /
NK014(pha)014:161: 'byung ba rim brtsegs stegs dang bcas //
NK014(pha)014:162: rdo rje rgya gram sa gzhi gang //
NK014(pha)014:165: 'og rdo rje rgya gram mig mang ris su gtams pa /
NK014(pha)014:166: zhes pa'i sna tshogs rdo rje dgos zhes gsungs na'ang /
NK014(pha)014:167: thal rgyud kyi lung de kho bos mthong ba'i rgyud
NK014(pha)014:168: kyi dpe la mi snang ba'i yod med kyang ma
NK014(pha)014:169: nges la / gal te yod srid kyang skyon med de /
NK014(pha)014:170: nyi seng gi lung rang gi rnam bshad drangs par /
NK014(pha)014:171: rgya gram la ni sa gzhi dang tshad med pa'i 'khor lo'i bar na gnas so //
NK014(pha)014:172: zhes pas rgya gram yod pa'i phyogs la'ang 'khor lo'i rtsibs kyis bsgribs nas mi mthong ba'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:173: bla ma'i lung don ni de ltar ma yin te /
NK014(pha)014:174: gal te yin na rgya gram zhes smos pa ha cang thal ba'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:177: pad+ma dang rgya gram thabs shes yin pas /
NK014(pha)014:178: pad+ma yod na rgya gram yang dgos par gsungs pas gnod do zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:180: sngar bshad pa ltar rgya gram 'khor lo'i 'og na yod par bzhed pa'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:181: de mi bzhed pa'i phyogs la'ang pad+ma dang 'khor lo thabs shes su 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:183: bde 'dus bskyed rdzogs 'bring po'i las byang las /
NK014(pha)014:184: de steng thabs kyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong 'bar //
NK014(pha)014:185: 'og tu shes rab pad+ma 'dab stong brdal //
NK014(pha)014:186: zhes 'og gzhi'i pad+ma dang gur gyi 'khor lo gnyis thabs shes su gsungs pa bzhin no //
NK014(pha)014:187: 'o na sna tshogs rdo rje byed pa'i phyogs la de'i bya tshul ji ltar zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:188: sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte ba gru bzhi pa /
NK014(pha)014:189: shar nub kyi rgyar cha chen bcu gnyis dang dpangs su cha chen gcig pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:191: dbus rwa sbom pa la cha chen gcig dang /
NK014(pha)014:193: g.yas g.yon gyi rwa gnyis sbom sa cha phran gsum dang /
NK014(pha)014:194: rtse mo rim gyis phra ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:196: rta babs sgo tshad gsum ma dang /
NK014(pha)014:198: gcig ma sogs la ltos nas cha chen bzhi dang /
NK014(pha)014:200: gnyis sogs gcig tu ma nges pa yin la /
NK014(pha)014:201: g.yas g.yon gyi rwa gnyis dbus rwa dang ring thung
NK014(pha)014:202: 'dra yang gug pa'i chas rtse mor ma sleb pa'o
NK014(pha)014:212: pany+tsa re kh+aa lnga steng nas steng du brtsegs pa'i lugs dang /
NK014(pha)014:213: phyi nang sbrags ma'i lugs gnyis las /
NK014(pha)014:217: ye shes rin chen rim brtsegs tshul //
NK014(pha)014:218: zhes gsungs pa ltar snga rabs pa phal cher bzhed /
NK014(pha)014:221: phyi ni rin chen lnga ru sbrags //
NK014(pha)014:223: bla ma las kun gyi phyi rol nag por bshad pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:225: kun gyi tha ma ljang gis bskor //
NK014(pha)014:227: tsags tsha sogs snga rabs pa 'ga' dang /
NK014(pha)014:228: sgrol chen yab sras sogs phyi rabs pa phal cher yang sbrags mar bzhed do //
NK014(pha)014:229: de la sgo'i thad du phyi ma bde bas 'dir yang re zhig phyi nang sbrags mar byas so //
NK014(pha)014:230: pany+tsa re kh+aa'i kha dog gi rim pa ni /
NK014(pha)014:232: sngo dang dkar dang ser dang dmar //
NK014(pha)014:233: kun gyi tha ma ljang gu ste //
NK014(pha)014:235: bde 'dus rigs brgya'i sgrub thabs las /
NK014(pha)014:238: srab 'thug cha chung gcig la re kh+aa lnga po
NK014(pha)014:239: gtso bo'i dbang gis nang nas rim pa bzhin mthing
NK014(pha)014:240: dkar ser dmar ljang gu ste /
NK014(pha)014:241: phan tshun reg la ma 'byar ba'i tshul du bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:242: yang gzhung gzhan las re kh+aa lnga po nas gang gis ma reg par gsungs pa la kha cig /
NK014(pha)014:243: cha chung gcig gi khyon la bar nas tshar re bzhag pa mi 'os zer na'ang /
NK014(pha)014:244: cha chung ni gtso bo'i khru gang yin la /
NK014(pha)014:245: nas ni de brgya re gyad gyi cha gcig yin pa'i phyir skyon med do //
NK014(pha)014:247: rta babs sgo tshad gsum ma dang /
NK014(pha)014:249: gcig ma la ltos te che 'bring chung gsum du bya ba 'thad kyis /
NK014(pha)014:250: phyogs gcig kho nar ngos bzung byas pa la shes byed med do //
NK014(pha)014:251: des na 'dir 'bring tshad kyi dbang gis cha phran bcu gsum du byas so //
NK014(pha)014:253: rtsig pa'i steng na yod pa'i lugs dang /
NK014(pha)014:254: phyi 'gram na yod pa'i lugs gnyis las /
NK014(pha)014:256: me long lta bu'i sgrub thabs dang /
NK014(pha)014:257: bde 'dus zhi ba zhe gnyis kyi sgrub thabs gnyis tshig don mthun par /
NK014(pha)014:258: kun nas bskor ba'i kha khyer la //
NK014(pha)014:259: rol mo sna tshogs sprin phung bzhin //
NK014(pha)014:260: zhes gsungs pa'i rjes su 'brangs par rlom nas byas par snang mod kyang /
NK014(pha)014:261: lung de'i dgongs pa de ltar ma yin pas mi rigs te /
NK014(pha)014:264: kun nas bskor ba'i phyi rol du //
NK014(pha)014:265: rdo rje'i kha khyer yang dag ldan //
NK014(pha)014:266: zhes 'dod snam la kha khyer zhes byas nas de
NK014(pha)014:267: gzhal yas khang gi phyir yod par bshad pa dang
NK014(pha)014:268: / gzhan yang nang gi lha snam la'ang kha khyer du bshad pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:269: sgo kha khyer dang bral ba bshad pa sogs mang du snang bas gnod pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:271: rtsig pa'i phyi ngos su 'gram stegs kyi tshul du yod par 'dod pa 'di legs te /
NK014(pha)014:272: bde 'dus rigs brgya'i sgrub thabs las /
NK014(pha)014:275: gshed mar gzhon nu rol pa'i sgom byang las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:276: phyi 'dod yon dmar pos 'gram stegs su bskor ba /
NK014(pha)014:278: be di kahzhesa pa'i sgra las drangs na'ang /
NK014(pha)014:282: stegs bu rnams la 'jug pa'i rgyu mtshan gyis so //
NK014(pha)014:283: dpangs cha phran gcig byed pa la shes byed med cing /
NK014(pha)014:285: dpangs su khru do yin la /
NK014(pha)014:287: 'chad 'gyur ltar rta babs kyis kyang ka ba sogs kyi dpags nus pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:288: 'dir cha phran gnyis par byas so //
NK014(pha)014:289: de yang bshad rgyud me long las /
NK014(pha)014:290: zla phyed rdo rje 'dod yon dang //
NK014(pha)014:292: snying po rol pa chen po'i rgyud las /
NK014(pha)014:293: zla phyed rdo rje mi 'jigs stobs //
NK014(pha)014:295: zhes pa'i 'dod snam gyi sgo khyud kyi mtshams dang /
NK014(pha)014:296: shar lho la sogs pa'i mtshams rnams su zla phyed rdo rje dang /
NK014(pha)014:297: phyogs bzhir gzugs la sogs pa'i lha mo 'god de /
NK014(pha)014:298: de'i tshul ni l+aa s+ye ma dkar mo me long /
NK014(pha)014:299: sgra ma dmar mo pi wam /
NK014(pha)014:300: dri ma sngon mo dri'i dung chos //
NK014(pha)014:301: ro ma ser mo g.yos kyis gang ba'i khar gzhong /
NK014(pha)014:302: reg bya ma dkar mo lha'i gos pany+tsa li ka thogs pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:303: rgyud las lha mo de lnga las ma gsungs shing /
NK014(pha)014:304: rdo rje las rim las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:305: gzugs la sogs pa mchod pa lnga //
NK014(pha)014:306: zhes pas de tsam gyi chog la gzhan du /
NK014(pha)014:308: longs spyod 'dod yon snam bu la //
NK014(pha)014:309: gzugs mdzes sgra snyan dri mchog dang //
NK014(pha)014:310: ro zhim yid 'ong chos rnams kyi //
NK014(pha)014:311: lha mo rnams kyis dgyes par rol //
NK014(pha)014:312: zhes chos kyi lha mo gsungs pa ltar na chos dbyings ma chos 'byung 'dzin pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:313: de dag kyang bsgom dbang du ni phyogs kun tu 'khrigs pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:315: gzugs sogs lha mos 'khrigs pa ste //
NK014(pha)014:316: sna tshogs mchod byed rol mo yis //
NK014(pha)014:317: bar snang khams kun sprin phung bzhin //
NK014(pha)014:320: 'ga' zhig 'dod snam gyi phyi rol na lcags chung gi tshul du yod gsungs na'ang /
NK014(pha)014:322: spyi yi rtse la pha gu gtod //
NK014(pha)014:325: ye shes brtsegs steng seng mgos gtams //
NK014(pha)014:326: mi 'jigs kha nas mu tig har //
NK014(pha)014:327: pha gu mdzes pa'i bad dang ldan //
NK014(pha)014:329: rtsig pa'i steng du pha gu gzhi ser po la
NK014(pha)014:330: rin po che'i phras mdzes par bad kyi tshul dang
NK014(pha)014:331: / seng mgo ni 'degs byed pad phur gyi tshul du yod pa sne la brkos pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:332: 'o na rtsig pa lnga steng nas steng du brtsegs
NK014(pha)014:333: pa mi 'dod pa'i lugs la la de'i snam bu'i
NK014(pha)014:335: lnga brtsegs su 'dod pa'i lugs la brtsegs pa dang po'i kha dog tu phreng bar bshad mod /
NK014(pha)014:336: 'dir ser po byed pa gang zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:337: he ru ka gal po'i brtags pa bdun par /
NK014(pha)014:338: 'dod yon dmar la pha gu ser //
NK014(pha)014:340: bde 'dus rigs brgya'i sgrub thabs las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:341: 'dod yon khyams dmar rin chen pha gu ser //
NK014(pha)014:343: sh+ra d+ha'i gzhung las de ltar 'byung bar grags so //
NK014(pha)014:344: seng mgo'i kha nas har gyi sgras /
NK014(pha)014:345: hahr do shal dang phreng ba la 'jug pas /
NK014(pha)014:346: mu tig gi phreng ba 'phyangs pa yin la /
NK014(pha)014:347: 'dir do shal phyed pa ma byas kyang chog ste /
NK014(pha)014:348: ar+d+ha ha ra zhes pa ma byung ba'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:349: bzhi pa d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa'i sa ni /
NK014(pha)014:350: pha gu'i steng du bre dpungs sam ka thung dang /
NK014(pha)014:351: des btegs pa'i gser gdung rnams ni go sla zhing /
NK014(pha)014:352: ka thung re re'i thad kyi gzhu dang gdung ma'i
NK014(pha)014:353: cha phran phyed tsam phyir 'bur ba'i gzer bu bzhi
NK014(pha)014:354: bzhi btab pa la gser skud dkris te phan tshun
NK014(pha)014:355: gcig nas gcig la 'phrad ngos su 'then pa ni
NK014(pha)014:356: gser gyi ska rags bzhi zhes grags so //
NK014(pha)014:357: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed ni gzhan dag ska rags dang
NK014(pha)014:358: po gnyis la chu srin ma ka ra'i mgo sbrags
NK014(pha)014:361: logs rgyan khyams mgo tsi pa tra'i //
NK014(pha)014:362: kha nas phreng ba rin chen ni //
NK014(pha)014:363: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa ba phyed gyur pa //
NK014(pha)014:364: zhes pas gser gdung gi steng du phyam gyi phyi
NK014(pha)014:365: ma dpangs cha phran phyed re 'phyar ba gser sked
NK014(pha)014:366: dang thad mnyam du 'ong bar byas nas phubs pa'i
NK014(pha)014:367: phyam sne rnams la bkod pa'i tsi pa tra'i kha
NK014(pha)014:368: nas d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa gser skud
NK014(pha)014:369: kyi phyi'i ngos su ring ba rnams pha gu la
NK014(pha)014:370: reg tu nye ba tsam du 'phyang ba ste /
NK014(pha)014:371: de la d+r+wa ba ni nor bu'i phreng ba tsi
NK014(pha)014:372: pa tra'i kha gcig nas gcig par sbrel te dpyangs
NK014(pha)014:374: d+r+wa phyed ni bgrangs phreng gi bcu shad lta bu
NK014(pha)014:375: kha'i dbus nas mthur du 'phyang ba'i rtse mo la
NK014(pha)014:376: nor bu sbom po dang ldan pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:378: rnga yab nor bu'i yu ba can dang /
NK014(pha)014:379: dril bu'i mthar nyi zla dang rnga yab kyi rlung
NK014(pha)014:380: bskyod can sogs kyang ji ltar rigs par bya ste
NK014(pha)014:382: pho brang de yi rgyan mchog kyang //
NK014(pha)014:383: nyi zla nor bu rin chen 'bar //
NK014(pha)014:384: bla re rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs //
NK014(pha)014:385: dar dang do shal mu tig phreng //
NK014(pha)014:386: dril bu dang ni rnga yab sogs //
NK014(pha)014:387: rol mo'i cha byad sna tshogs brgyan //
NK014(pha)014:388: zhes gsungs pa'i rgyan rnams gzhan du'ang ci rigs 'god pa 'byung mod kyi /
NK014(pha)014:390: yang lha rje so'i zhal nas /
NK014(pha)014:392: mtha' ma'i 'dab mas kun g.yogs pa'i //
NK014(pha)014:393: ye shes brtsegs steng seng mgos gtams //
NK014(pha)014:394: mi 'jigs kha nas mu tig har //
NK014(pha)014:395: pha gu mdzes pa'i bad dang ldan //
NK014(pha)014:397: zhes pa'i mu tig gi ha ra dang /
NK014(pha)014:398: rkang pa tha ma'i d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed gnyis don gcig pa yin te /
NK014(pha)014:402: pha gu la d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed 'phyangs la /
NK014(pha)014:403: bre phul gyi snam bur dar ras las grub pa'i
NK014(pha)014:404: shar bur sngon po dang dkar po 'phyang ba yin
NK014(pha)014:407: zhes gsungs pa de d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed
NK014(pha)014:408: pa la dgongs pa ma yin pas mi rigs so
NK014(pha)014:410: pha gu las rtsig pa'i phyir 'phyangs pa'i mu tig gi d+r+wa ba de /
NK014(pha)014:411: rtsig pa'i ya tha na bad kyi tshul du yod
NK014(pha)014:412: pa'i pha gu gdong gi tshul can de nyid kyi
NK014(pha)014:413: mgul 'khor ba'i tshul du 'dod pa bzhed pa ste
NK014(pha)014:415: ye shes rtsig steng seng mgos gtams //
NK014(pha)014:416: mi 'jigs kha nas mu tig har //
NK014(pha)014:417: pha gu mdzes pa'i bad dang ldan //
NK014(pha)014:418: zhes rkang pa gsum pa de'i don yin no //
NK014(pha)014:421: gang gis mtha' ma'i 'dab mas kun g.yogs pa'i //
NK014(pha)014:422: zhes pa la snyegs pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:424: des kun nas g.yogs pa'i 'og tu /
NK014(pha)014:425: mas nas yar rtsig pa dang seng mgo las 'phyang ba'i mu 'phreng dang /
NK014(pha)014:426: pha gu rnams rim par brtsegs pa'i steng du /
NK014(pha)014:427: d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa rnams ni /
NK014(pha)014:428: bya 'dab des mgul 'khor ba'i tshul du yod ces pa'i don te /
NK014(pha)014:429: don 'di la dgongs nas rje sgro phug pa'i gsung sgros riim par brgyud pa las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:432: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed kyi gseb /
NK014(pha)014:433: ces ka thung dang d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed kyi sa gcig tu mdzad pa yin no //
NK014(pha)014:434: de'i phyir rig pa'i bstan bcos las /
NK014(pha)014:435: spyir btang bstan bcos nges pa las /
NK014(pha)014:436: bye brag stobs dang ldan par brjod //
NK014(pha)014:438: spyi bye brag 'doms na bye brag dbang btsan pa'i rig pas /
NK014(pha)014:439: spyi btang tsam du dkyil 'khor phal che bar d+r+wa
NK014(pha)014:440: ba d+r+wa phyed gnyis pha gu'am bre phul gyi snam
NK014(pha)014:441: bu gang rigs la 'dogs pa las gnyis ka 'dogs
NK014(pha)014:442: pa'i phyag len 'byung ba bden na'ang /
NK014(pha)014:443: bye brag tu sngar drangs pa'i 'od rim gyis lung dang /
NK014(pha)014:444: slob dpon rgyal ba bzang po dpal sbas kyi sgyu 'phrul 'od kyi phyag las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:445: seng mgo'i kha nas mu tig 'phreng //
NK014(pha)014:446: pha gu d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed dang //
NK014(pha)014:447: zhes sogs 'di nyid kyi thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK014(pha)014:448: man ngag phal che bar mu 'phreng dang d+r+wa ba
NK014(pha)014:449: d+r+wa phyed gnyis tha dad du gsungs pa'i lung ches
NK014(pha)014:450: gsal ba mang du bzhugs pa'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:451: dar ras las grub pa'i shar bu zhes pa'ang mi rigs te /
NK014(pha)014:453: ye shes rin po che'i phreng ba dang /
NK014(pha)014:456: zhes shar bu'i rgyu rin po cher bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:458: khyams kyi phyam steng du cha chung gcig gi dpangs la babs sam byi rtser grags pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:459: de'i steng du bya 'dab bkal ba khyams las kyang
NK014(pha)014:460: cha chung phyed gnyis tsam phyir 'phyar 'dod snam dang
NK014(pha)014:461: kha da chad du bya gsungs pa ltar ram /
NK014(pha)014:462: de las cung zad ring bar byas na'ang /
NK014(pha)014:464: chu 'dod snam gyi phyir 'babs pa bkod pa legs pas so //
NK014(pha)014:466: gser thog g.yu thog sogs dang rnam pa 'dra ba ste /
NK014(pha)014:467: gyo mo'i wa kha 'og dang steng du blta ba'i
NK014(pha)014:468: khyad par gyis pho gyo mo gyo zhes grags shing
NK014(pha)014:469: / de yang snga rabs pa rnams pho gyo'i mtha' dgag la khyung mgo byas pa bya dang /
NK014(pha)014:470: mo gyo'i mtha' 'phyang la pad 'dab phyed pa'i rnam
NK014(pha)014:471: pa lta bu byas pas 'dab ma zhes grags par
NK014(pha)014:472: bzhed / phyis kyi lo ts+aa ba rgya gar mkhas
NK014(pha)014:473: pa'i lag rgyun gzigs pa dag phyam sna dang byi
NK014(pha)014:474: rtse'i phyi ngos rin po ches mdzes par byas pa
NK014(pha)014:475: la bya 'dab steng 'og ces bzhed pa'ang yod do
NK014(pha)014:476: bzhed / // drug pa shar bu ni /
NK014(pha)014:477: bya 'dab gyi nang tsam nas spyi blugs mgo mthur
NK014(pha)014:478: bstan lta bu'i shar bu'i phreng ba dkar pos kun
NK014(pha)014:479: tu bskor ba rtse mo phyams kyi ma mtha'i thad
NK014(pha)014:482: nor bu mig gsum mgo thur du bstan nas bsgrigs pa lta bu'ang yod par 'dod do //
NK014(pha)014:485: gdung sna gnon pa la rin po che'i pu shu mchod rten rtsigs su bsgrigs pa /
NK014(pha)014:487: rtsig pa'i drang thad nas thog mthil nas rin po
NK014(pha)014:488: che'i pang leb dkar po gyen lang cha phran gcig
NK014(pha)014:489: pa g.yas g.yon du mtho dman gyi stag so ris
NK014(pha)014:490: rim pa bzhi bzhi yod pa /
NK014(pha)014:491: rgyang nas bltas na mchod rten 'dra ba la pu shu mchod rten rtsegs su grags shing /
NK014(pha)014:492: pad+ma phyed par gsungs pa yang 'dab ma yan gar ba zhig ma yin te /
NK014(pha)014:493: 'dab ma brgyad pa'i pad+ma la gzhung thig btab nas
NK014(pha)014:494: bcad pa'i kha mthur du bstan nas bsgrigs pa lta
NK014(pha)014:495: bu ste mchod rten rtsigs dang gnad gcig pa yin
NK014(pha)014:496: zhes gsungs so // gzhung kha cig tu /
NK014(pha)014:497: rin po che'i d+r+wa mig seng ma kha dog sna tshogs kyi spras par 'dod pa'ang snang ngo //
NK014(pha)014:498: bzhi pa thog 'bub la rim pa gsum 'bub pa'i 'thad pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:502: phug na ka ba brgyad po yis //
NK014(pha)014:503: gdung chen bzhi yi rtse nas btegs //
NK014(pha)014:504: gdung chen bzhi yi re mig kyang //
NK014(pha)014:505: phyam rtsa nyi shu brgyad kyis bkab //
NK014(pha)014:506: de bzhin gral thog ci rigs pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:508: bar skabs kyi mkhas pa dag na re /
NK014(pha)014:509: gser gdung gi gdung bzhi mig mang ris su btang la /
NK014(pha)014:510: re mig phyi ma brgyad po phub re mig dbus
NK014(pha)014:511: ma phyur bur byas te thog nyis rim kho nar
NK014(pha)014:512: nges zhes gsungs pa ni lung de'i dgongs pa ma
NK014(pha)014:513: yin te / gal te yin na /
NK014(pha)014:515: phyi dbyibs mchod rten du bya ba yang gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:516: thog steng du mchod rten brjid can 'gel ba'am /
NK014(pha)014:517: gzhan du na mchod rten chung ngu thog mthil du
NK014(pha)014:518: bzhag pa lta bu zhig ma gtogs bya dka' ba'i
NK014(pha)014:519: phyir dang / bka' brgyad lta bu gdung bzhi mig
NK014(pha)014:520: mang ris su phub pa'i so so'i nang khongs su
NK014(pha)014:521: gzhal yas khang dgu tshom byas pa de'i tshe dbang
NK014(pha)014:522: mo'i khyams bya sa med pa'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:523: khyad par sgyu 'phrul ba rnams ni 'od rim gyi lung khas blangs dgos la de ltar na /
NK014(pha)014:525: yang thog mtho dman rim par ldan //
NK014(pha)014:526: zhes pa'i yang thog gi don ni /
NK014(pha)014:529: yang thog zhes 'jig rten du tha snyad grags pa ltar yin pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:530: steng thog la mtho dam'i rim pa 'dod dgos na /
NK014(pha)014:531: de ltar yang byar mi rung ba'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:532: yang 'od rim gyi lung don de la kha cig /
NK014(pha)014:533: tha snyad sems phyir bum pa gcig /
NK014(pha)014:534: rma bya'i mdangs ltar ci yang snang //
NK014(pha)014:535: mtho dman tshad med bya 'dab ldan //
NK014(pha)014:536: thugs rjes kun snyoms khyab phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:537: yang thog mtho dman rim ldan par //
NK014(pha)014:538: mtha' ma'i 'dab ma kun g.yogs pa'i //
NK014(pha)014:539: zhes dbus bum pa zlum po'i bya 'dab dang /
NK014(pha)014:540: mtha' ma steng 'og thog gi bya 'dab ste /
NK014(pha)014:541: de gnyis la dgongs nas yang thog mtho dman zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir nyis thog go zer /
NK014(pha)014:542: de ltar na khang pa thog gcig ma rnams kyang
NK014(pha)014:543: steng thog can du thal ba'i phyir mi rigs so
NK014(pha)014:545: dbus bum pa zlum po kha dog cir yang snang ba mtho dam'i tshad dpag tu med pa /
NK014(pha)014:546: de'ang thugs rjes kun la snyoms khyab kyi rtags su bya 'dab can no //
NK014(pha)014:547: de'i steng du bre mtshon pa'i phyur bu'i thog gru bzhi pa la'ang bya 'dab bkal ba na /
NK014(pha)014:548: yang thog mtho dman rim par ldan //
NK014(pha)014:550: rgya cher 'grel las phyi dbyibs mchod rten du gsungs pa'ii lung don kyang grub bo //
NK014(pha)014:551: de bas na bya 'dab 'og ma 'og ma las
NK014(pha)014:552: steng ma steng ma rgya je chung du song ba'i
NK014(pha)014:554: steng ma steng ma la 'og ma 'og ma phyi
NK014(pha)014:555: 'khor ba'i tshul du yod la de'i phyir 'og thog
NK014(pha)014:556: gi bya 'dab la mtha' ma'i 'dab ma zhes gsungs
NK014(pha)014:557: so // yang bar skabs kyi zur lugs pa 'ga' zhig /
NK014(pha)014:558: dbus bum pa zlum po 'khyil ba'i don gur gyi
NK014(pha)014:559: rnam par bzhed pa la'ang 'od rim gyi lung 'dis
NK014(pha)014:561: gnyis pa ji ltar 'bubs lugs la thog rim gsum las /
NK014(pha)014:562: dang po 'og thog ni 'dir gzhung rnams su 'degs
NK014(pha)014:563: byed kyi ka ba gsal bar ma gsungs pas rtsig
NK014(pha)014:564: nang nas seng gdung zur nas ring ba dang /
NK014(pha)014:565: ngos nas thung ba btang ba'i shing brtsegs kyi bkod
NK014(pha)014:566: pa ji ltar rigs pas gdung zlum btegs nas ya
NK014(pha)014:569: 'di'i ka ba rnams 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng rdor phreng
NK014(pha)014:570: gi steng nas 'dzugs dgos pas thog mar nang gi
NK014(pha)014:572: sgo khyud kyi bar stod gru bzhi pa la sgo
NK014(pha)014:573: phugs dang 'gram gyi phyi sgo logs gnyis kyi bar
NK014(pha)014:574: la sgo g.yab ces zer la /
NK014(pha)014:575: de gnyis ka'i spyi ming ni sgo khang ngo //
NK014(pha)014:576: de la 'dir phyi nang gi them skas 'dzug dgos
NK014(pha)014:577: pa'i gnad kyis sgo g.yab las sgo phugs cha phran
NK014(pha)014:578: gcig dang / de las kyang khyams cha phran gcig gi mtho bar bya dgos pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:579: nang gi khyams dang phyi 'dod snam dpangs mnyam par song bas /
NK014(pha)014:580: de'i phyir rtsig pa'i dpangs kyang stegs bu gru bzhi
NK014(pha)014:581: pa gcig gi steng nas cha phran bcu gcig bslang
NK014(pha)014:583: khyams zheng cha phran gsum par bya ba sogs ni go sla la /
NK014(pha)014:584: 'on kyang lha rnams sgeg pa bzhed pa'i phyogs la
NK014(pha)014:585: khyams cha phran gsum pa de las phyir cha phran
NK014(pha)014:586: gcig dor nas cha phran gnyis pa'i lha snam bya
NK014(pha)014:587: / de la'ang khyad 'byed mtho dman cung zad byas na legs gsung ngo //
NK014(pha)014:588: 'dir sgo las khyams dang de las gru chad /
NK014(pha)014:589: de las rtsibs kyi phyi'i mu khyud rdor phreng /
NK014(pha)014:591: de las lte ba rnams cha phran re res spags pa ni /
NK014(pha)014:592: theg pa gzhan las 'dir 'phar ba'i don la ste /
NK014(pha)014:595: sgo la sogs pa'i rim pa dang //
NK014(pha)014:597: glo 'bur gru chad las thig gang gis mtho ba
NK014(pha)014:598: dang rtsibs mchan rdor 'phreng las de tsam gyi dma'
NK014(pha)014:599: bar byas pa ni gzhung las ma bshad kyang khyad
NK014(pha)014:600: 'byed tsam mo // thig skud gang la tshad ji tsam zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:601: cha phran gcig gi cha lnga ste /
NK014(pha)014:602: he ru ka 'dus pa'i rgyud las /
NK014(pha)014:603: sbom phra sgo yi nyi shu cha //
NK014(pha)014:605: glo 'bur gyi dbyibs ni gru chad las cha chung
NK014(pha)014:606: gcig po phyir 'phyar ba'ii phib chung gi rnam pa'o
NK014(pha)014:608: 'og gi gru chad khyams stod kyi tshul du cung zad mtho bas /
NK014(pha)014:609: steng gi gru chad bya 'dab kyi tshul yod do //
NK014(pha)014:610: 'og gi glo 'a bur gru chad kyi phyogs bzhi na khri stegs kyi tshul du yod la /
NK014(pha)014:611: steng gi glo 'bur ni bya 'dab kyi steng na lcog bzhi'i tshul du yod do //
NK014(pha)014:613: de la phyis kyi bla ma mkhas pa dag na re /
NK014(pha)014:614: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi mu khyud zlum po'i phyi
NK014(pha)014:615: rim du phyogs bzhi'i lha snam des bcad pas zur
NK014(pha)014:616: bzhir gru chad ring thung du byung ba de la
NK014(pha)014:617: zer gyi / 'og gi gru chad khyams stod kyi
NK014(pha)014:618: tshul du cung zad mtho ba 'ong don ci yang
NK014(pha)014:619: zer gyi / med / steng gi gzhal yas khang
NK014(pha)014:620: gi thog gis khyab pa'i steng du gru chad ni
NK014(pha)014:622: 'og gi glo 'bur khri stegs kyi tshul du yod na der su zhig gi sdod sa yin /
NK014(pha)014:624: steng gi glo 'bur bya 'dab kyi steng du lcog rgyab pa 'di 'dra i srid /
NK014(pha)014:626: 'dir sgo khang phyir 'bur ba gzhal yas khang gi
NK014(pha)014:627: rtsig pa dang cha phran gnyis kyi bar 'gyangs yod
NK014(pha)014:629: blos bslang gi dkyil 'khor ma mthong ba'i skyon du snang /
NK014(pha)014:630: zhes sogs brgal brtag mang du mdzad do //
NK014(pha)014:631: de la steng gi gru chad dang /
NK014(pha)014:632: steng gi glo 'bur gyi 'dod pa de dag la dgag pa mdzad pa bden mod kyi /
NK014(pha)014:633: de ltar na'ang mkhas pa'i gsungs de dag la'ang gsung
NK014(pha)014:634: rab dang ltag 'chus ches pa'i skyon 'di dag mthong
NK014(pha)014:635: ste / zhi ba bsdus pa lta bu bar khyams
NK014(pha)014:636: med cing 'khor lo'i mu khyud kyi steng nas bum
NK014(pha)014:637: pa zlum po'i phyur bur 'degs byed kyi ka ba
NK014(pha)014:639: 'og tu rdor 'phreng las 'phyar ba'i glo 'bur dang /
NK014(pha)014:640: sgo'i 'gro 'ong bde khyad kyi cha chen bzhi pa'i
NK014(pha)014:641: mtha' nas cha phran gnyis tsam phyir dor ba'i nang
NK014(pha)014:642: du rtsibs kyi mu khyud bskor dgos pas /
NK014(pha)014:643: ngos kyi khyams thung sar gser gdung dang gdung zlum thug la khad pa zhig 'ong la /
NK014(pha)014:644: de'i dbang gi steng du gdung zlum kha'i bum pa zlum po'i rtsig pa dang pu shu gnyis /
NK014(pha)014:645: ngos kyi dbus su thug 'gro bas thog mthil gyi
NK014(pha)014:646: zur bzhir gru chad ring thung du byung ba'i gru
NK014(pha)014:648: gsang rdzogs ma h+aa'i sgom rim las /
NK014(pha)014:649: 'khor ba'i g.yul las rgyal zhing bdud bzhi bcom pa'i brdar gru chad bzhir rgyal mtshan /
NK014(pha)014:650: zhes gsungs pa'i rgyal mtshan de yang nang du 'dzug dgos par thal ba'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:651: pha rol pos bya 'dab kyi tshul du yod par
NK014(pha)014:652: 'dod pa'i skyon ngan pa de la dgag pa mdzad
NK014(pha)014:653: thang ba lam mdzad 'dug pa'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:654: bya 'dab kyi steng du lcog brgyab pa de 'dra
NK014(pha)014:655: ba 'dir mi 'ong yang lar nas mi srid pa
NK014(pha)014:656: ma yin te / bsam yas kyi gtsug lag khang la sogs pa de ltar snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:657: khyad par 'og gi gru chad khyams stod kyi tshul du cung zad mtho ba 'ong don med na /
NK014(pha)014:659: sgo la sogs pa'i rim pa dang //
NK014(pha)014:660: zhes spags par gsungs pa'ang mi rigs par 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:662: de khri stegs kyi tshul du yod par mi rigs na /
NK014(pha)014:664: spyan lnga'i glo 'bur mdzes pa las //
NK014(pha)014:665: phyag na rdo rje sngo skya'i mdog /
NK014(pha)014:668: glo 'bur bzhi la rigs yab yum 'khril ba'i tshul /
NK014(pha)014:669: zhes glo 'bur la nang sems bzhi 'god par bshad pa'ang mi rigs par thal ba'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:670: sgo bzhi kho na lhag pa'i glo 'bur du bzhed na /
NK014(pha)014:671: bde 'dus zhi ba 'bring po'i sgom rim las /
NK014(pha)014:672: ye shes gcig gi nang du kun tshangs pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:673: gru chad la mkhar thabs glo 'bur du 'gyur ro zhes dang /
NK014(pha)014:675: rtsa ba bzhi'i phyir glo 'bur du snang ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:676: zhes 'khor lo'i rtsibs bzhi phyi de na glo 'bur yod par bshad pa dang 'gal ba'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:678: glo 'bur cha phran sgo khyams gnyis //
NK014(pha)014:679: zhes sgo khang gi 'bur thabs la cha phran gcig las med par 'gyur bas /
NK014(pha)014:680: cha phran gnyis yod par bshad pa dang 'gal snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:681: yang rje sgrol g.yung gnyis kyi t+ai kar /
NK014(pha)014:682: rtsa rgyud kyi dbang du lha med pa'i khang stong bzhi /
NK014(pha)014:684: 'grel chung las lha yod par bshad la /
NK014(pha)014:685: de rtsa rgyud kyi 'grel pa yin pa'i phyir 'thad par ma mthong ngo //
NK014(pha)014:686: des na glo 'bur gyi don 'di la snga rabs
NK014(pha)014:687: pa phal che bas phyogs re kho na la bshad
NK014(pha)014:688: pa mdzad pas 'then khyer byung ba yin la /
NK014(pha)014:689: kho bo ni 'di ltar sems te /
NK014(pha)014:690: snying po rol pa chen po'i rgyud las /
NK014(pha)014:691: lhag pa'i ye shes rin po che //
NK014(pha)014:692: nyi shu rtsa lnga'i rtags rnams kyis //
NK014(pha)014:693: rang gi dkyil 'khor mdzes bya ba //
NK014(pha)014:696: drug pa'i ye shes snying rje ngo bo nyid gzhi dang /
NK014(pha)014:697: de re re la'ang bzhi bzhir gsal bas /
NK014(pha)014:698: rgyas pa'i dbang du pho brang rtsibs bzhi lngar snang ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:699: 'bring bsdus ltar rtsa ba bzhi'i phyir glo 'bur du snang ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:700: zhes pas rtsa ba'i ye shes lnga ni /
NK014(pha)014:701: dbus bum pa zlum po dang sgo bzhi'i glo 'bur bzhi'o //
NK014(pha)014:702: de re re'ang lhag pa'i ye shes bzhi bzhi rtsa
NK014(pha)014:703: ba dang bcas pa'i lnga lnga ste nyi shu rtsa
NK014(pha)014:704: lnga'o // de'i rtags su dbus bum pa zlum po
NK014(pha)014:705: chos dbyings ye shes kyi phyag rgyar gyur pa'i lhag
NK014(pha)014:707: sgo bzhi ni me long ye shes la sogs pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:708: re re yang rtsig pa rim pa lnga lngas phye bas nyi shu rtsa lngar 'gyur ro //
NK014(pha)014:709: de ltar yang rje sgro phug pa chen po'i gsung rgyun las /
NK014(pha)014:710: ye shes re re'ang lhag pa'i ye shes bzhi bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK014(pha)014:713: ye shes re re yang lnga lngas khyad par du byas pa /
NK014(pha)014:716: glo 'bur bzhi yang mkhar thabs tshul //
NK014(pha)014:717: zhes pa'i mkhar thabs kyis sgras phyi'i glo 'bur kho na nges so snyam na ma yin te /
NK014(pha)014:718: nang gi glo 'bur yang mkhar thabs su sngar drangs
NK014(pha)014:719: pa'i bde 'dus kyi lung gis grub pa'i phyir dang
NK014(pha)014:720: de'i don kyang / lha rjes mang mkhar ba seng ha pra b+has /
NK014(pha)014:721: gru chad la ba gam gyi tshul du phyir 'phyar
NK014(pha)014:722: ba de mkhar gyi 'bur thabs lta bu'i tshul du
NK014(pha)014:723: yod do zhes gsungs pa ltar te /
NK014(pha)014:724: mkhar dngos yin mi dgos la /
NK014(pha)014:725: gal te dgos na pu shu mchod rten tshad ldan bya dgos par thal lo //
NK014(pha)014:727: seng gdung gi btegs pa'i gdung zlum steng du rtsig dpangs cha phran bdun las /
NK014(pha)014:730: de'i steng nang gi rdo phreng la brten pa'i ka
NK014(pha)014:731: ba cha chen lnga dang cha phran gcig gis btegs
NK014(pha)014:733: tal gdung bzhi sdom pa'i dpangs cha phran gcig /
NK014(pha)014:734: de steng phyam dang bya 'dab la gcig gi ste
NK014(pha)014:735: khyon cha chen gnyis dang cha phran gcig tu 'gyur
NK014(pha)014:736: bas / gsang rdzogs kyi thig rtsa slob dpon gyis mdzad pa las /
NK014(pha)014:737: bum rten la ni cha phran gcig /
NK014(pha)014:738: bum pa cha chen gnyis tshad do //
NK014(pha)014:739: zhes pa dang tshad mtshungs so //
NK014(pha)014:740: bum pa'i phyogs bzhir bum sgo byas na nang mthong
NK014(pha)014:741: dkar phyir mdzes pa zhig 'ong bas grub na bya
NK014(pha)014:742: / gdung zlum steng du gdung bzhi brgyugs pa'i bar seng de dgag pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:743: gdung sna brgyad la rin po che'am pad+ma lta bu
NK014(pha)014:744: ci mdzes brkos la de dang bar ma chad pa'i
NK014(pha)014:746: bya 'dab kyi sna las rin po che'i d+r+wa ba
NK014(pha)014:747: d+r+wa phyed ma byas kyang chog la byas kyang mi
NK014(pha)014:749: phyi dbyibs rgyal khab rgya phubs can mdzad na'ang /
NK014(pha)014:752: rtse mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK014(pha)014:753: 'khor ma lus pa thams cad so so ma yin
NK014(pha)014:754: ngo bo nyid gcig pa'i ye shes kun tu 'khyil
NK014(pha)014:757: spyi bo shin tu 'khyil bar gnas //
NK014(pha)014:759: bshad rgyud ye shes snying po las /
NK014(pha)014:760: rtse mo gcig pa ru 'dus pa dbyer med pa'i ro dang ldan pas thig le zlum pa /
NK014(pha)014:763: gru bzhi spyi bo 'khyil snang ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:764: zhes sogs rtsa bshad kun las zlum por bshad pa dang 'gal lo //
NK014(pha)014:765: zlum po de yang bum pa'i rnam pa can te /
NK014(pha)014:767: bum pa'i tshul du dbyibs rdo rje rgya gram mig mang ris 'khyil ba /
NK014(pha)014:770: bum pa'i rtse mo chos kyi tog /
NK014(pha)014:771: rma bya'i mdangs ltar bkra ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:774: tha snyad sems phyir bum pa gcig /
NK014(pha)014:775: ces sogs rnam pa du mar dbyibs bum par bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:776: 'di yi ka ba dang tal gdung bzhi gtong tshul ni /
NK014(pha)014:777: phug na ka ba brgyad po yis //
NK014(pha)014:778: zhes pa'i dgongs pa yin la /
NK014(pha)014:779: gdung zlum btang ba sangs rgyas gsang ba'i gzhung 'di las mi 'byung na'ang /
NK014(pha)014:781: ka ba brgyad kyi steng du rdo rje'i phreng ba zlum pos yongs su bskor ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:782: zhes pa ltar 'dir yang bum pa zlum po'i gnad kyis bya dgos mod /
NK014(pha)014:783: 'on kyang de ka bas mi 'degs pa ni bye brag dbang btsan par byas pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:784: gzhan dag nang ka la ka gdan mi byed par 'dod kyang /
NK014(pha)014:785: 'dir ka gdan bum pa cha phran gcig dang /
NK014(pha)014:786: de'i steng du ka ba gzhu dang bcas pa bya dgos te /
NK014(pha)014:788: ka gdan bsnyen gnas klu chen brgyad /
NK014(pha)014:789: ka ba 'phags lam phyogs skyong brgyad /
NK014(pha)014:790: ka gzhu rnam thar lha chen brgyad /
NK014(pha)014:791: gdung bzhi mi 'jigs rgyal chen bzhi //
NK014(pha)014:793: gzhung 'di'i rjes su 'brangs te bu ston rin po
NK014(pha)014:794: ches kyang nang gi ka ba la ka gdan mdzad
NK014(pha)014:795: pa la / mkhas pa dag na re /
NK014(pha)014:796: nang gi ka ba la ka gdan byed pa'ang phreng ba'i dgongs pa ma yin te /
NK014(pha)014:797: rta babs kyi ka ba rnams ni stegs gru bzhi pa dang bum pa la gnas /
NK014(pha)014:798: zhes pa'i sgras nges par bzung ba'i tshig gis logs su bkar ba'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:799: zhes phreng ba mkhan po'i lung gis gnod byed 'bebs par mdzad mod /
NK014(pha)014:800: de ni pan grub gcig gi rjes su 'brangs pa
NK014(pha)014:801: la gcig shos dang mi mthun pa'i gnod byed 'bebs
NK014(pha)014:803: shin tu rigs pa ma mthong ste /
NK014(pha)014:805: kho bo cag gi phar zlog ste /
NK014(pha)014:806: nang ka la ka gdan med pa'ang sangs rgyas gsang ba'i dgongs pa ma yin te /
NK014(pha)014:807: ka gdan bsnyen gnas klu chen brgyad //
NK014(pha)014:808: ces nang ka la ka gdan bya bar gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:809: zhes smras na mtshungs pa'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:810: a b+ha ya dang sangs rgyas gsang ba gnyis pan grub yin mnyam las /
NK014(pha)014:811: da rung sangs rgyas gsang ba la 'gran du med par grub pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:812: gzhan yang khyod kyis dpyod pa dang ldan pa su zhig dga' ba skye bar 'gyur zhes dang /
NK014(pha)014:813: mkhas pa gzhan dag gis kyang lung de sangs rgyas gsang ba'i yin par bardzusa mar snang zhing /
NK014(pha)014:814: zhes gsungs pa rnams dbang che ba tsam du zad de /
NK014(pha)014:815: rdzun lung yin pa'i gtan tshigs 'chad rgyu ma byung 'dug pa'i phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:816: yang mkhas pa 'ga' zhig na re /
NK014(pha)014:817: sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad zer ba'i chos don ni /
NK014(pha)014:820: lha chen brgyad kyi ka ba sogs rnam dag mang
NK014(pha)014:821: bas bod kyi rnying ma ba rnams kyis byas par
NK014(pha)014:823: zhes gsungs pa yang phyogs gtam ste /
NK014(pha)014:824: zhi khang dang khro khang bshad pas bod mar gyur na /
NK014(pha)014:825: lha zhi khro yang bod mar thal ba'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:826: rnam dag mang bas bod mar gyur na /
NK014(pha)014:827: dus kyi 'khor lo'i dkyil 'khor lta bu phyi nang
NK014(pha)014:828: gi dag sbyor shin tu mang ba bshad pa de
NK014(pha)014:829: dag kyang bod mar ba'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:830: bod kyis byas par mkhas pa rnams bzhed ces pa la'ang snying po med de /
NK014(pha)014:831: bu ston sogs snga rabs kyi mkhas grub chen po
NK014(pha)014:832: rnams rnam dag tu bzhed par so so'i gsung rab
NK014(pha)014:833: la bltas pas shes pa'i phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:834: des na rang gi zhe 'dod dang ma mthun pa
NK014(pha)014:835: tsam zhig rgyu mtshan du byas te bod mar 'dod
NK014(pha)014:836: pa de dag snying po med par shes par bya'o
NK014(pha)014:837: // yang rdo rje las rim las /
NK014(pha)014:838: rdo rje nor bus nyer mdzes pa'i //
NK014(pha)014:839: ka ba phyag rgya'i gdung bzhir sbyar //
NK014(pha)014:840: zhes pas 'dir rdo rjes mtshan pa'i nor bu rin
NK014(pha)014:841: po che'i ka ba phyogs mdog can brgyad po phyag
NK014(pha)014:842: rgya bzhi mtshon pa'i tal gdung bzhi la sbyar ba
NK014(pha)014:843: ste / bde 'dus zhi ba'i rtsa rgyud las /
NK014(pha)014:844: rdo rje'i ka bas brgyan pa /
NK014(pha)014:847: rdo rjes mtshan zhing legs mdzad pa'i //
NK014(pha)014:848: ka ba brgyad ni nang du bri //
NK014(pha)014:851: dbus bum pa zlum po'i re'u mig dbus ma ma
NK014(pha)014:852: phub par bzhag pa de'i steng du bres mtshon pa'i
NK014(pha)014:853: steng khang gru bzhi pa 'bubs te /
NK014(pha)014:854: de'i tshul ni mthong kha'i zur bzhir btsug pa ka ba cha phran phyed bzhir /
NK014(pha)014:855: gzhu dang gdung la cha phran phyed re /
NK014(pha)014:856: de'i steng du cha phran gcig pa'i rgya phubs 'gebs /
NK014(pha)014:857: 'di dang bum zlum gyi bya 'dab kyi rtsa ba
NK014(pha)014:858: gnon pa'i lan kan ni tshan gcig tu ma nges
NK014(pha)014:859: kyang / cha phran gcig las che ba mi legs so //
NK014(pha)014:860: rgya phub kyi 'og tu bla bre phub /
NK014(pha)014:861: steng gi dbus su pad+ma la gnas pa'i 'khor lo
NK014(pha)014:862: rim pa bcu gsum gyi steng na rat+na'i gdugs kyis
NK014(pha)014:863: mdzes shing tog dang bcas pa bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:864: de ltar yang rdo rje me long las /
NK014(pha)014:865: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor byas shing //
NK014(pha)014:866: nyon mongs tshad pa'i gdung ba sel //
NK014(pha)014:867: thugs rje gdugs kyi 'khor lo bstan //
NK014(pha)014:868: ma lus gcig tu 'dus pa ni //
NK014(pha)014:872: rtse rgyan rnam dag mchod rten la //
NK014(pha)014:873: srog shing sku gsung thugs su bstan //
NK014(pha)014:874: 'khor lo sa yi khyad par yin //
NK014(pha)014:875: char khebs thugs rje chen po ste //
NK014(pha)014:876: 'phan ni mchod pa'i lha mo la //
NK014(pha)014:877: dril bu stong pa nyid kyi sgra //
NK014(pha)014:878: zla tshes thabs dang shes rab yin //
NK014(pha)014:879: tog ni mi nub rgyal mtshan no //
NK014(pha)014:880: zhes gsungs pa'i 'phan dang dril bu ni char khebs las 'phyangs la /
NK014(pha)014:881: zla tshes ni dril bu'i rlung bskyod do //
NK014(pha)014:882: rdo rje rin po che'i tog ni /
NK014(pha)014:883: kha cig rgyu nor bu rin po che'i tog rdo rje las grub par 'dod /
NK014(pha)014:884: kha cig rgyu nor bu las byas pa'i phyag mtshan rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i dbyibs su 'dod /
NK014(pha)014:885: phal cher nor bu dang rdo rje gnyis ka'i dbyibs dgos par 'dod /
NK014(pha)014:887: bum pa tog dang bcas pa'i rnam pa ga ti rar grags pa nyid te /
NK014(pha)014:888: gal te rdo rje'i rnam pa dgos na'ang rwa phreng
NK014(pha)014:889: nyid rdo rje'i rwa'i rnam pa yin pas de tsam
NK014(pha)014:890: la bya'i / phyag mtshan gyi rdo rje'i rnam pa gsal dod pa mi dgos gsungs /
NK014(pha)014:891: de dag las 'dir snying po rol pa chen po'i rgyud du /
NK014(pha)014:892: rtse mo nor bu 'bar ba la //
NK014(pha)014:893: rigs kyi mtshan ma rgyan du byas //
NK014(pha)014:894: zhes gsungs pa'i lung don la lugs gsum pa nyid nye bar mngon no //
NK014(pha)014:895: de ltar phyi dbyibs mchod rten du bya tshul 'di la kha cig 'di snyam du /
NK014(pha)014:897: re zhig byang chub chen po las //
NK014(pha)014:898: dran dang yang dag rdzu 'phrul dbang //
NK014(pha)014:899: bang rim bzhi yi don du bzhed //
NK014(pha)014:900: bum stegs stobs te bum pa ni //
NK014(pha)014:901: byang chub lam yin bye brag ni //
NK014(pha)014:902: 'phags pa'i lam du shes par bya //
NK014(pha)014:903: zhes pas gzhal yas khang dngos gzhi'i steng du bang
NK014(pha)014:904: rim bzhi bum rten bum pa bre sogs byang chen
NK014(pha)014:905: mchod rten gyi rnam par bya bar bshad pa dang
NK014(pha)014:907: de ltar bshad pa bden mod /
NK014(pha)014:910: gzhal yas phyi'i don rtags rnams //
NK014(pha)014:911: mchod rten brgyad sogs bstan pa ni //
NK014(pha)014:912: sdug bsngal brgyad sgrol mdzad pa brgyad //
NK014(pha)014:913: ces byang chen kho nar ma nges pa'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:914: lung snga ma'i re zhig ces pa'i nus pas kyang thon pa'i phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:915: des na rgyud 'grel bshad sgrub thabs rnams nas bum pa'i dbyibs su bshad la /
NK014(pha)014:916: bang rim bya ba ma bshad pa'i phyir 'dir ma byas so //
NK014(pha)014:917: de ltar na'ang chos don dang mi 'gal te /
NK014(pha)014:918: myang 'das mchod rten du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:921: gru bzhi lham pa mdzes par snang //
NK014(pha)014:922: rin chen sna bzhi'i rgyu las grub //
NK014(pha)014:925: b+han+d+ha gsar rnying brtsegs pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK014(pha)014:926: yon tan che rgyas gru bzhi lham pa'i dbyibs //
NK014(pha)014:929: gru bzhi lham pa shin tu mdzes //
NK014(pha)014:930: zhes gsungs pa'ii lham pa'i don kha cig /
NK014(pha)014:931: steng 'og gru bzhi par nges pas gzhal yas khang
NK014(pha)014:932: gi 'og thog man chad rgya dpangs mnyam zer na'ang
NK014(pha)014:934: lham pa'i don zlum po ma yin pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:935: ya yo med pa la bshad pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:936: nor bu rgyas pa'i le'u lnga par /
NK014(pha)014:937: ras kha tshar ma chad pa rgya mod pa gru do gru bzhi lham pa la /
NK014(pha)014:938: zhes gsungs pas lung de'i don de ltar ma yin zhes mkhas pa dag gsungs so //
NK014(pha)014:939: 'dir gzhal yas khang 'og thog gi gser gdung man chad la nang gi cha phyed dpangs dang /
NK014(pha)014:940: rtse mo'i tog man chad rta babs kyi ka ba'i phyi mtha' dang rgya dpangs mnyam pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:941: gzhan du na sngar bshad pa ltar rtsig pa mtho
NK014(pha)014:942: dman gyi tshad che 'bring chung gsum las dpangs mtha'
NK014(pha)014:943: gcig tu nges pa ma yin no //
NK014(pha)014:945: phyogs bzhi'i rtsig pa'i dbus su bris cha la ji ltar yod pa ltar /
NK014(pha)014:946: tshangs thig gi g.yas g.yon du cha chung gnyis gnyis
NK014(pha)014:947: te sdom pas cha chen gcig pa'i har bton pa
NK014(pha)014:949: mtshams de'i rtsig sne nas mdun du cha chen re 'then pa sgo khyud /
NK014(pha)014:950: de'i sne nas g.yas g.yon du cha phran gnyes re ngos su bkyed de 'then pa sgo 'gram /
NK014(pha)014:951: de'i ngos nas mdun du cha phran gnyis 'then pa ni sgo logs so //
NK014(pha)014:952: khyud 'gram logs sum ka'i rtsig dpangs ni sgo yi har dang mnyam la /
NK014(pha)014:953: de'i tshad rtsig pa mtho dman 'bring gsum gyi dbang las gcig tu ma nges kyang /
NK014(pha)014:954: 'dir 'bring tshad kyi dbang du byas nas cha phran
NK014(pha)014:955: bcu dang cha phran gcig gi sum gnyis su byas
NK014(pha)014:956: so // 'dir mkhas mchog dag gis mdzad zer ba'i dong sprugs kyi dkyil chog tu /
NK014(pha)014:957: 'gram logs dang bral ba'i sgo byas te /
NK014(pha)014:960: chu srin kha na chu srin 'bar //
NK014(pha)014:961: rta babs sgo las sum 'gyur ro //
NK014(pha)014:964: ka ba'i rtse nas 'thon rtse mo //
NK014(pha)014:965: sna tshogs rdo rje 'od po che //
NK014(pha)014:966: zhes pa'i lung gnyis dang dgongs pa mthun zhes mchan gyis gsal bar byas so //
NK014(pha)014:967: de ni dong sprugs rang gi lag len man ngag
NK014(pha)014:968: brgyud pa can yin na mi 'gal ba srid mod
NK014(pha)014:969: / de las gzhan du sgyu 'phrul gyi rgyud sgrub thabs rnams las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:971: zhes 'gram dang logs kyi ming dngos su ma gsung
NK014(pha)014:972: pas bya mi dgos sam snyam du bsams nas de
NK014(pha)014:973: ltar byas pa yin na mi 'thad de /
NK014(pha)014:975: khor yug gsum pa'i zheng tshad la rta babs phyed dang gsum du bya bar bshad pa ltar /
NK014(pha)014:976: rang gi yi ger yang rdor cha phran gnyis pa
NK014(pha)014:977: la sogs par byas pa dang nang 'gal ba'i phyir
NK014(pha)014:979: khyud sogs pho brang zheng dang mnyam //
NK014(pha)014:980: zhes gsungs pas skabs 'dir khyud ni 'gram la bya ste /
NK014(pha)014:981: de ltar na 'gram logs kyi tshad gang zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:982: de cha phran gnyis par ston pa la /
NK014(pha)014:984: tshangs thig g.yas g.yon cha chen phyed //
NK014(pha)014:985: ces pho brang gi phyogs re'i zheng tshad gsungs pa 'dis bstan pas na /
NK014(pha)014:986: 'gram logs tshad dang bcas te gsungs pa'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:988: nang gi sgo kun cha phran gnyis //
NK014(pha)014:989: khyud dang logs ni re re'o //
NK014(pha)014:990: de la 'di snyam du 'gram gyi ming la khyud zer ba nor ro zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:991: gzhung khungs gzhan dag las kyang gcig tu ma nges pa 'di ltar 'byung ste /
NK014(pha)014:992: bde 'dus zhi ba rigs brgya'i gter dpe dngos las /
NK014(pha)014:993: dbus brgyad cha la sgo 'gram dang //
NK014(pha)014:994: zhes khyud la 'gram du gsungs shing /
NK014(pha)014:995: dus 'khor gyi 'grel chen dri med 'od las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:996: 'gram dang logs kyi tha snyad go ldog tu gsungs pa'i phyir mtha' gcig tu ma nges so //
NK014(pha)014:997: 'on kyang thig gi pan+dir+thi'i dpe dag pa byung na da dung dpyad par bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:998: de ma zad sum pa dang rgya ston gyi phyag
NK014(pha)014:999: bzhed ltar rdo rje rin chen gyis bris pa'i chos
NK014(pha)014:1000: don gyi thig chog las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:1001: sgo ni dkyil 'khor brgyad cha gcig /
NK014(pha)014:1002: de yi phyed la sgo 'gram bya //
NK014(pha)014:1003: zhes sogs sngon gyi slob dpon grub pa'i dbang phyug
NK014(pha)014:1004: rnams kyis mdzad pa'i thig chog rnams su'ang 'gram logs
NK014(pha)014:1007: sgo khyud ces pa ngos dang logs dang 'gram ya phubs la sogs pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:1008: zhes pas 'gram logs yod par grub bo //
NK014(pha)014:1009: de ltar na lugs 'di la sgo khang spyi'i ming la sgo khyud ces 'bod par snang ste /
NK014(pha)014:1011: sgo khyud re re bzhin sgo sum sgrigs re res brgyan pa /
NK014(pha)014:1012: zhes pa'ang ya phubs 'degs byed kyi ka bas sum ral lta bur gyur pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:1014: bka' brgyad zhi dkyil la'ang 'gram logs bya mi dgos par thal /
NK014(pha)014:1015: bde 'dus zhi ba zhe gnyis kyi sgrub thabs las /
NK014(pha)014:1016: rnam thar bzhi yi sgo khyud la //
NK014(pha)014:1017: zhes pa las ma gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:1020: rtsa ba dbus cha gnyis te mtha' gnyis dor ba
NK014(pha)014:1021: sgo rgyan dang bcas bya dbus brgyad cha la sgo
NK014(pha)014:1022: 'gram dang / ya phubs logs dang sgo khyud rol pa tshon sna lngas /
NK014(pha)014:1025: cha gnyis sgo ste gsum pa khyud //
NK014(pha)014:1026: bzhi pa 'gram ste lnga pa logs //
NK014(pha)014:1027: drug pa nam mkha' stong pa yin //
NK014(pha)014:1028: bdun dang brgyad la ka ba bya //
NK014(pha)014:1029: zhes gsungs pa dang 'gal ba'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:1030: phreng ba dang mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho'i lung des kyang lung mi 'grub ste /
NK014(pha)014:1031: lung de gnyis ni logs dang ka ba'i bar na mun snang med par 'dod pa'i lung yin gyi /
NK014(pha)014:1032: 'gram logs mi 'dod pa'i lung ma yin par sngon
NK014(pha)014:1033: gyi mkhas grub rnams kyis gtan la phab tshar ba
NK014(pha)014:1034: ltar yin pas mang du mi spro'o //
NK014(pha)014:1035: sgo logs kyi rtsig pa'i nang nas cha chung phyed
NK014(pha)014:1036: gnyis nang du phyiin pa'i sar ya phubs 'degs byed
NK014(pha)014:1037: kyi ka ba zheng cha phran phyed /
NK014(pha)014:1038: dpangs phyed dang brgyad yod pa zhig btsugs pa'i nang mtha' dang /
NK014(pha)014:1039: sgo khyud kyi rtsig pa'i nang mtha' drang thad du 'ong bar bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:1040: de'i steng du gdung dpangs cha phran phyed pa zhig
NK014(pha)014:1041: sgo logs kyi rtsig pa la gdung khung brus nas
NK014(pha)014:1042: btsugs te 'gebs / ka ba 'og ma'i ka thog
NK014(pha)014:1043: ka bzhag gi ka thung cha phran phyed gnyis dang
NK014(pha)014:1044: btsugs te 'gebs / / gdung la phyed bya /
NK014(pha)014:1045: ka thung gi bar la rdo rje bcu gcig 'greng
NK014(pha)014:1046: bur bslang ba'i d+r+wa mig dang gdung gi steng du
NK014(pha)014:1047: ya phubs kyi rtsig dpangs cha phran gyi sum gnyis
NK014(pha)014:1049: 'dir kha cig ya phubs kyi steng du rtsig pa mi 'khor ba bzhed na'ang /
NK014(pha)014:1051: ya phubs logs dang sgo khyud rol pa tshon sna lngas /
NK014(pha)014:1053: zhes pas lung des 'khor ba legs so //
NK014(pha)014:1054: bcu gcig rdo rje'i d+r+wa mig byed pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK014(pha)014:1056: sgo khang sgo srung khang pa ste //
NK014(pha)014:1057: steng gi ma rig mun pa las //
NK014(pha)014:1058: ye shes mthong khang dbye ba'i phyir //
NK014(pha)014:1059: bcu gcig rdo rje d+r+wa mig byed //
NK014(pha)014:1061: de'i tshad kyang gsang rdzogs las /
NK014(pha)014:1062: bcu gcig rdo rje'i cha phran gcig /
NK014(pha)014:1063: ces pa'i bar stod cha phran phyed gnyis las cha
NK014(pha)014:1064: phran gyi bzhi cha re tsam pa'i rdo rje'i brten
NK014(pha)014:1065: sa yas mas gnyis ka la gdung las nang du
NK014(pha)014:1066: cung zad bskum pa re btang ba'i bar du rdo
NK014(pha)014:1067: rje'i dpangs la cha phran gcig re bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:1068: lha rje mang mkhar ba sogs 'di dang rta rkang
NK014(pha)014:1069: gi snam bu'i rdo rje'i don gcig tu mdzad nas
NK014(pha)014:1070: / de nas rdo rje bcu gcig gi grangs nges mdzad pa sogs ni 'thad pa ma mthong ste /
NK014(pha)014:1071: slob dpon pad+mas mdzad pa'i gsang rdzogs ma h+aa'i sgom rim las /
NK014(pha)014:1072: sgo khang bzhi mthing nag grib sos brgyan pa la /
NK014(pha)014:1073: ya phub rdo rje bcu gcig gis gnam mthong gsal ba /
NK014(pha)014:1074: zhes gsungs pa dang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:1076: kha cig sgo khyud kyi nang dang /
NK014(pha)014:1077: kha cig khyud 'gram gyi mtshams dang /
NK014(pha)014:1078: la la dag phyi nang gnyis kar 'dzug par 'dod pa'i lugs gsum las /
NK014(pha)014:1079: 'dir sgo khyud kyi nang du 'dzug pa nyid rje bla ma'i dgongs pa yin te legs so //
NK014(pha)014:1080: de ltar na bu ston rin po ches /
NK014(pha)014:1082: sgo rnams kun gyi nang du ni //
NK014(pha)014:1083: sgo bsrung rnams ni dgod par bya //
NK014(pha)014:1084: zhes pas sgo khyud kyi phyir yang sgo glegs 'dzug dgos pa gsungs pas gnod do zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:1085: mi gnod de sgo bsrung gi phyi rol na sgo yod kyang /
NK014(pha)014:1086: de la sgo glegs dgos par ma nges te /
NK014(pha)014:1088: slob dpon tshul khrims bskyang gis /
NK014(pha)014:1089: rta babs la'ang sgo dang po las gsungs pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:1091: sgo la steng dang 'og yin te //
NK014(pha)014:1092: 'og gi sgo dang sgo khang can //
NK014(pha)014:1093: steng ni skas dang glang rgyab sogs //
NK014(pha)014:1094: ji ltar mdzes pa'i tshul du bzhengs //
NK014(pha)014:1095: zhes glang rgyab kyang sgor gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:1096: rta babs dang glang rgyab sogs la'ang sgo glegs gzhug dgos na ha cang thal lo //
NK014(pha)014:1099: lam brgyad rim par bgrod pa yis //
NK014(pha)014:1100: 'bras bu'i yon tan kun rdzogs pas //
NK014(pha)014:1101: rta babs rgyu 'bras bcu drug bstan //
NK014(pha)014:1102: zhes pas rnam thar gyi theg pa brgyad la sbyangs pa rtogs pa'i rtags su rgyu'i rta babs dang /
NK014(pha)014:1103: theg brgyad kyi grub mtha'i yon tan brgyad rdzogs pa'i
NK014(pha)014:1104: rtags su 'bras bu'i rta babs brgyad de bcu drug
NK014(pha)014:1105: go // de ltar yang sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las /
NK014(pha)014:1106: theg pa brgyad kyi nges 'byung ba'am //
NK014(pha)014:1107: rgyu 'bras cha yis phyi nang gis //
NK014(pha)014:1108: them skas brgyad du rnam par snang //
NK014(pha)014:1109: zhes pa'i rgyu'i rta babs bstan /
NK014(pha)014:1111: de yi grub pa'i mtha' rdzogs pa'i //
NK014(pha)014:1112: yon tan brgyad phyir rta rkang dang //
NK014(pha)014:1113: chu skyes sgrom dang za ra tshags //
NK014(pha)014:1115: khyung mgo mdzes pas rim par 'khrigs //
NK014(pha)014:1116: zhes pa'i 'bras bu'i rta babs bstan no //
NK014(pha)014:1118: dang po rgyu'i rta babs ni /
NK014(pha)014:1121: rdo rje gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud rnams tshig don mthun par 'di skad du /
NK014(pha)014:1123: de phyir ye shes sgo bzhir shar //
NK014(pha)014:1124: der 'gro lam stegs brgyad dang ldan //
NK014(pha)014:1125: rta babs brgyad du 'gyur ba yin //
NK014(pha)014:1128: sgo khyud bzhi ldan rta babs bcas //
NK014(pha)014:1129: bsti gnas lam gyi bgrod phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:1131: 'di la snga rabs kyi bla ma phal cher sgo khang dang khyams las sgo cung zad mtho bas /
NK014(pha)014:1133: phyi nas bzhi ste brgyad do gsungs /
NK014(pha)014:1134: rje se ston chen po ni /
NK014(pha)014:1135: phyogs bzhir rta babs zhon gyi sa nas sgor 'jug
NK014(pha)014:1136: pa'i bar du them skas gnyis gnyis te brgyad do
NK014(pha)014:1137: gsungs / de gnyis ka mi rigs te /
NK014(pha)014:1138: sgom them la phyi nang nas skas 'dzug sa bkod pa shin tu mi bde ba'i phyir dang /
NK014(pha)014:1139: phyogs re re them skas gnyis re yod pa sdom
NK014(pha)014:1140: pas rta babs brgyad du 'gyur na rgyan gyi rta
NK014(pha)014:1141: babs la'ang mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:1143: 'grel pa nyi seng mar sgo re re la them
NK014(pha)014:1144: skas gnyis gnyis su gsungs pa'i dgongs pa'o zhe na
NK014(pha)014:1145: ma yin te / 'grel pa'i dgongs pa ni sgo
NK014(pha)014:1146: re re la skas phyi nang gnyis yod pa la
NK014(pha)014:1147: ma yin te / dgongs pa'i phyir / 'o na gang zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:1148: sngon gyi mkhas grub chen po rnams kyis /
NK014(pha)014:1150: nang nas bzhi zhes gsungs pa'i don sgo g.yab dang
NK014(pha)014:1151: sgo phubs kyi mtshams su phyi'i them skas bzhi dang
NK014(pha)014:1152: / sgo phugs dang khyams kyi mtshams su nang gi them skas bzhi 'dzug pa yin no //
NK014(pha)014:1153: 'dir phyis kyi mkhas pa dag na re /
NK014(pha)014:1154: gsar ma'i rong pa chos mgon dang rnying ma'i rog
NK014(pha)014:1155: shes rab 'od sogs kyis sgo'i phyir rta babs zhon
NK014(pha)014:1156: gyi tshul du yod pas rta babs su 'dod pa
NK014(pha)014:1158: bu ston dang stag tshang lo ts+aa ba sogs kyis
NK014(pha)014:1159: bkag pa la legs so dang bcas te smra ba
NK014(pha)014:1160: dang / mkhas dbang la la dag rta babs zhon
NK014(pha)014:1161: gyi sa yin pas rta babs zhes pa legs sbyar
NK014(pha)014:1162: gyi tshig don la ma zhugs so //
NK014(pha)014:1164: bris kyi skabs kyi rta babs 'di nyid them skas
NK014(pha)014:1165: su 'dod mkhan yod na ni nges par 'khrul la
NK014(pha)014:1168: t+wa ra na zhes pa mngon par 'phyang ba'i don
NK014(pha)014:1169: yin pas them skas la dpyangs pa'i don mi tshang
NK014(pha)014:1170: ba bden yang / gzhan du nyon mongs med pa
NK014(pha)014:1171: la'ang 'jug pas de'i phyag rgyar gyur pa'i phyir dang
NK014(pha)014:1172: ba bden yang / / rnam pa gcig tu na
NK014(pha)014:1173: tu ring ta gam ma na zhes pa rta la
NK014(pha)014:1174: ba bden yang / / bya bas / pho brang
NK014(pha)014:1175: du 'jug pa na 'di dag rta babs zhon gyi
NK014(pha)014:1176: stegs yin pas na de skad du grags so zhes
NK014(pha)014:1177: sngon gyi lo ts+aa ba chen po dag gsungs pa'i
NK014(pha)014:1178: ba bden yang / / bya bas / phyir dang / phyogs bcu mun sel las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:1179: t+wa ra na'i sgra bar snang gi rgyan dang /
NK014(pha)014:1181: rta babs zhon gyi stegs dang /
NK014(pha)014:1182: them skas la 'jug pa gsungs pa ltar yin pas
NK014(pha)014:1183: legs sbyar gyi sgra la ma zhugs pa'i skyon med
NK014(pha)014:1184: la / de med pa nyid kyi gegs snga ma'ang sel lo //
NK014(pha)014:1186: lam stegs brgyad ni 'phags lam dang //
NK014(pha)014:1187: theg pa brgyad dang rnam thar brgyad //
NK014(pha)014:1188: ces them skas phyi nang gnyis thun mong gi don rtags dang /
NK014(pha)014:1189: sgo stegs rta babs bzhi po ni /
NK014(pha)014:1190: gsum ni khams gsum bzhi po ni /
NK014(pha)014:1192: zhes phyi nang gi them skas re re la rim
NK014(pha)014:1193: pa bzhi bzhir yod pa'i don rtags kyang gsungs so
NK014(pha)014:1194: // gnyis pa 'bras bu'i rta babs ni /
NK014(pha)014:1195: sgo logs kyi phyi zur bris cha'i ka ba'i sne
NK014(pha)014:1196: mo bzhis slebs pa'i steng du phyi nang gi ka
NK014(pha)014:1198: 'o na ka gdan dang bcas pa'i ka dpangs cha phran bdun pa byas pa 'di ni /
NK014(pha)014:1200: rta babs kyi ka ba rtsig pa'i thig la 'thon cing /
NK014(pha)014:1202: zhes pa'i phyogs ni mi rigs te /
NK014(pha)014:1203: gzhal yas khang las cung zad ring bar rta babs
NK014(pha)014:1204: kyi ka ba rnams re re bzhi stegs bu gru
NK014(pha)014:1205: bzhi pa la gnas pa'i phyir sa mnyam po la
NK014(pha)014:1206: gnas pa nyid kyis stegs bu dang 'brel ba bzhin
NK014(pha)014:1207: mthong bas / stegs bu'i phyi ngos su 'di rnams bri bar rigs so //
NK014(pha)014:1208: zhes ka ba cha chung bdun pa bkag pas mi rigs so zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:1209: phreng ba'i dgongs pa ni de ltar ma yin te /
NK014(pha)014:1211: phreng ba'i phyogs snga ma de'i zhe 'dod la /
NK014(pha)014:1212: rta babs kyi ka ba rtsig pa'i thig la thon pa bya dgos te /
NK014(pha)014:1213: ka dpangs la cha chung bdun dgos la /
NK014(pha)014:1214: de 'dod rnams kyi cha chung gnyis po ma bsnan na mi longs pa'i phyir snyam du bsam mo //
NK014(pha)014:1215: 'dod pa de phreng ba mkhan pos dgag pa na /
NK014(pha)014:1216: ka ba cha chung bdun dgos kyang /
NK014(pha)014:1217: bris kyi ka ba cha chung lnga po de bslangs
NK014(pha)014:1218: pa'i tshe re re bzhin stegs bu gru bzhi pa
NK014(pha)014:1219: bum pa dang bcas pa'i cha chung gnyis la gnas
NK014(pha)014:1220: pa'i phyir / ka gdan de 'dod snam dang dpangs khad mnyam du song bas /
NK014(pha)014:1221: rgyang nas bltas na ka ba cha chung lnga po
NK014(pha)014:1222: de 'dod snam gyi steng du btsugs pa lta bur
NK014(pha)014:1223: 'brel bar mthong ba zhig 'ong bas bris kyi dus
NK014(pha)014:1224: su ka gdan bri mi dgos la /
NK014(pha)014:1225: gal te bris na rta babs kyi ka ba nang
NK014(pha)014:1226: ma gnyis kyi 'dzug pa'ang gzhal yas khang las cha
NK014(pha)014:1227: phran gnyis kyi bar yod pas cung zad ring ba'i
NK014(pha)014:1229: rtsig pa'i thig las thon pa byas na bslangs pa'i
NK014(pha)014:1230: dus su'ang rtsig pa la reg pa'i sar 'dzugs dgos
NK014(pha)014:1231: sam snyam pa'i dogs pa de skye srid pa'i phyir
NK014(pha)014:1232: / lag len de 'dra legs pa ma yin no //
NK014(pha)014:1233: de'i phyir stegs bu'i phyir ngos su 'di rnams bri bar bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:1235: 'dir mkhas pa 'ga' zhig gi ka ba gzhal yas
NK014(pha)014:1236: khang las cung zad ring ba'i don ka ba'i dpangs
NK014(pha)014:1237: la byas te gzhal yas khang shin tu dma' bar
NK014(pha)014:1238: byas pa dang / gzhan dag ka gdan ka ba'i
NK014(pha)014:1239: dpangs cha chung lnga pa'i khog tu brtsibs la sogs
NK014(pha)014:1240: pa rnams ni 'thad par ma mthong ngo //
NK014(pha)014:1241: de ltar na'ang stegs bu gru bzhi pa la gnas pa'i phyir zhes pa las mi 'byung ba la /
NK014(pha)014:1242: 'dir bum pa dang bcas pa'i cha chung gnyis par byed par mi rigs so zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:1243: de nas ka gdan gru bzhi pa des bum pa yang mtshon dgos pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:1244: phreng ba nyid las rta babs kyi ka ba rnams
NK014(pha)014:1245: ni stegs bu gru bzhi pa dang bum pa la
NK014(pha)014:1248: stegs bu bum pa las byung ba'i //
NK014(pha)014:1249: rta babs ka ba drang por bya //
NK014(pha)014:1251: ka ba bzhi po'i steng du rta babs 'degs byed
NK014(pha)014:1252: kyi gdung yod pa dang med pa'i phyogs gnyis las
NK014(pha)014:1253: / 'dir gdung yod pa'i phyogs bstan te //
NK014(pha)014:1255: sgo khang phyir zur bzhi po na //
NK014(pha)014:1256: ka ba bzhi bzhi'i gdung rtsa ni //
NK014(pha)014:1257: brgyad brgyad btegs pa rta babs rmangs //
NK014(pha)014:1258: ka gdan ka gzhu ci rigs pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:1260: gdung 'di'i dpangs ni cha phran gcig pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:1262: gdung dang rta babs brgyad cha mnyam //
NK014(pha)014:1264: rgyab gdung gi sne nang ma gnyis sgo 'gram gyi
NK014(pha)014:1265: rtsig pa'i phyi mthar gdung khung brus nas btang bas
NK014(pha)014:1266: dum bu gnyis su song bas na gdung lngar 'gyur
NK014(pha)014:1268: gdung bzhi bsnol mar btang ba ni /
NK014(pha)014:1269: bden bzhi bsam gtan bzhi dang ldan //
NK014(pha)014:1270: zhes gdung bzhir gsungs pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:1271: rgyab kyi gdung zlum po gnyis po de rgyab phyogs
NK014(pha)014:1272: kyi gdung zhes rigs bsdus nas gsungs pa yin pa'i
NK014(pha)014:1275: rta babs bzhi dang ka ba brgyad //
NK014(pha)014:1276: ces rta babs kyi ka ba bcu drug po phyogs
NK014(pha)014:1277: re re la ka ba gnyis gnyis rigs bsdus te
NK014(pha)014:1280: sgo khyud bzhi ru brjod pa yin //
NK014(pha)014:1281: zhes pa'ang phyogs re re la sgo khyud gnyis gnyis
NK014(pha)014:1282: yod kyang rigs bsdus nas bzhir gsungs pa ltar ro
NK014(pha)014:1283: // de'i phyir slob dpon gyis nang gi gdung ma la /
NK014(pha)014:1284: gdung chen bzhi yi rtse nas btegs //
NK014(pha)014:1287: brgyad brgyad btegs pa zhes gsungs pa'ang 'di lta bu'i 'khrul gzhi skye srid pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:1288: des na 'dir gdung bzhi ni rigs bsdus pa yin la /
NK014(pha)014:1289: bsnol mar btang ba ni gdung rtsa brgyad po bsnol ba la dgongs so //
NK014(pha)014:1290: rgyab mdun gyi gdung ka ba'i phyir cha phran re re thal ba'i 'og tu /
NK014(pha)014:1291: glang po che'i steng du seng ge'i lag gcig gis glang po'i spyi bor mnan cing /
NK014(pha)014:1292: dpung pa gcig btegs te 'phyar ba /
NK014(pha)014:1293: de yi kha nas rin po che 'phyang ba ste /
NK014(pha)014:1295: seng ge ba glang rnams kyis brgyan //
NK014(pha)014:1296: zhes pa dang mthun la bla ma dgongs 'dus las
NK014(pha)014:1297: glang chen seng ge'i rkang pa gnyis kyis mnan cing
NK014(pha)014:1298: lang ba'i lag gnyis kyis gdung 'degs pa gsungs so
NK014(pha)014:1299: // gdung gi steng du rta babs bya ste /
NK014(pha)014:1300: 'di la snga rabs pa 'ga' zhig na re /
NK014(pha)014:1301: rta rkang ni rta babs 'degs pa'i ka ba /
NK014(pha)014:1304: za ra tshags ni gdung shams /
NK014(pha)014:1306: chun 'phyang ni rdo rje rin chen dang dar 'phyangs /
NK014(pha)014:1307: phreng ba ni mu phreng ngam mun pa'i kha rgyan shar bu /
NK014(pha)014:1308: khyung mgo ni bre logs bzhi la'o //
NK014(pha)014:1309: mdzes pas rim par 'khrigs pa ni /
NK014(pha)014:1313: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i snam bu bcu gcig po ste /
NK014(pha)014:1314: rim par rtsig pa yon tan brgyad ldan no zer ba ni /
NK014(pha)014:1315: rgyud sgrub thabs thams cad nas rta babs snam bu brgyad du bshad pa dor nas /
NK014(pha)014:1316: phreng bar snam du bcu gcig pa bris snang ba'i phyir shin tu mi rigs so //
NK014(pha)014:1317: yang chos don 'brel ba byed pa kha cig /
NK014(pha)014:1319: chu skyes dang sgrom gnyis rgyab phubs kyi pho gyo mo gyo /
NK014(pha)014:1322: phreng ba bzhi po gyo mo kha nas 'phyongs la /
NK014(pha)014:1323: khyung mgo ni rgya phubs kyi steng g.yas g.yon gnyis na'o zer ba'ang sngar ltar 'khrul lo //
NK014(pha)014:1324: yang lha rje rog steng rgyan ni zag pa med
NK014(pha)014:1325: pa'i rin po che dang gos sna tshogs kyi bla
NK014(pha)014:1330: phreng ba sna tshogs pas brgyan cing /
NK014(pha)014:1331: sna tshogs pa'i khyung mgo dag gis mdzes par gyur pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:1333: zhabs dang ma chags za ra tshags //
NK014(pha)014:1335: de yang 'thad pa ma mthong ste /
NK014(pha)014:1336: rgyan gyi rta babs rkang dor ba'i phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:1337: yang mkhas grub chen po dag gi phyag len du grags pa las /
NK014(pha)014:1338: d+r+wa mig dpangs cha phran gcig dang /
NK014(pha)014:1339: chu skyes dang pha gu gnyis la phyed phyed /
NK014(pha)014:1341: yang chu skyes phyed dang sgrom phyed dang gnyis dang /
NK014(pha)014:1342: pha gu dang khyung mgo gnyis la re re bzhed ces 'byung na'ang /
NK014(pha)014:1345: rta babs brgyad po cha mnyam zhing //
NK014(pha)014:1347: chu skyes pha gu sgrom gsum ldabs pa'ang /
NK014(pha)014:1348: rgyud sgrub thabs rnams su gsungs pa ma mthong ngam /
NK014(pha)014:1350: gser gdung ka rgyan mtha' dang mnyam //
NK014(pha)014:1351: rta rkang dang ni chu skyes gnyis //
NK014(pha)014:1352: de la cha phran gcig gi ring //
NK014(pha)014:1353: rin chen de las gnyis kyi thung //
NK014(pha)014:1354: sgrom bu de las gcig gi ring //
NK014(pha)014:1355: zar tshags pad+ma mda' yab gsum //
NK014(pha)014:1356: rim bzhin cha phran re re bskum //
NK014(pha)014:1358: sgyu 'phrul gyi lugs 'dir mi rigs te /
NK014(pha)014:1359: 'dir gser gdung snam bu brgyad kyi nang du grangs la /
NK014(pha)014:1361: gdung dang rta babs brgyad cha mnyam //
NK014(pha)014:1362: zhes pa'i dang sgras tha dad du phye ba'i phyir ro //
NK014(pha)014:1363: yang lha rje se ston chen pos /
NK014(pha)014:1364: snam bu dang po ka rgyan mtha' dang mnyam /
NK014(pha)014:1365: de nas rim par gcig 'phyar gcig bsdu ba'i rim pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:1366: khyung mgo cha phran gnyis bskum pa'o gsungs /
NK014(pha)014:1367: de ltar na sgril 'phyang gi gzhi bar stong la 'phyar dang /
NK014(pha)014:1368: de'i steng 'og gi snam bu gnyis la bskum gyi res babs pas /
NK014(pha)014:1370: sgril 'phyang dang sham bu bzhed pa'ang /
NK014(pha)014:1376: rta rkang chu skyes pha gu sgrom //
NK014(pha)014:1377: snam 'phyong seng mgo shar bu phreng //
NK014(pha)014:1378: zhes drang nas de ltar bzhed la /
NK014(pha)014:1379: g.yung t+aika tu'ang de dang mthun par gsungs so //
NK014(pha)014:1380: de'i don gzhan ni spyi dang mthun la /
NK014(pha)014:1381: phreng ba ni pu shu'i phreng bas bskor ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:1382: 'on kyang las rim gyi dpe rnams lung de dang
NK014(pha)014:1383: de'i dod thub gang yang ma mthong bas da dung
NK014(pha)014:1384: dpyad par bya'o // 'o na 'dir ji ltar bya zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:1385: rang gi rje bla ma'i dgongs pas /
NK014(pha)014:1386: rta babs sgo tshad gnyis la snam bu brgyad du phye ba la rim bzhin /
NK014(pha)014:1387: rta rkang gzhi sngon po la gser gyi rdo rje 'greng bur bsgrigs pa /
NK014(pha)014:1388: chu skyes ni pad+ma dmar po /
NK014(pha)014:1389: sgrom gyi mtha' dang dbus su ka chung bzhi btsugs
NK014(pha)014:1390: pa la sgrom leb kha dog ci mdzes bcug pa'o
NK014(pha)014:1391: // snam bu de gsum mdun dang g.yas g.yon gsum
NK014(pha)014:1392: po sgor mo sgo khang gi rtsig pa la cha
NK014(pha)014:1393: phran res ma reg pa bya ste /
NK014(pha)014:1394: bris cha'i skabs su sgo logs dang ya phubs kyi
NK014(pha)014:1395: rtsig pa'i phyir mun pa pa ti 'khor ba de
NK014(pha)014:1396: yin la / sh+rad+d+h+aa dang smri tis kyang /
NK014(pha)014:1397: rta babs ya phubs dag las ni //
NK014(pha)014:1400: de yang rta babs 'degs byed kyi gdung rgyab la
NK014(pha)014:1401: dum bu gnyis po de sgo khang gi rtsig pa
NK014(pha)014:1403: de'i steng du snam bu 'khor mor rgyug gam snyam na /
NK014(pha)014:1404: mun pa'i cha chung gcig po'i sa la mi rgyug pa yin no //
NK014(pha)014:1405: snam bu gsum po de rnams nang khong stong can gyi khog tu ka ba dang /
NK014(pha)014:1406: des btegs pa'i gdung btang ste /
NK014(pha)014:1407: sgo khang gi thog dang cha mnyam du dbub bo //
NK014(pha)014:1408: de'i steng du ka ba brgyad dang /
NK014(pha)014:1409: des btegs pa'i gdung bzhi sgo mor btang ba la /
NK014(pha)014:1410: sgril 'phyang ma gtogs pa'i snam bu gzhan rnams ka
NK014(pha)014:1411: ba'i phyi ngos la srab 'thug thig skud gang tsam
NK014(pha)014:1412: gyi pang leb zur langs brtsegs pa lta bu'i snam
NK014(pha)014:1414: khyung mgo steng nas phubs pas zar tshags yan chad
NK014(pha)014:1415: sgo steng gi ba gam bsil ba'i khang bur gyur
NK014(pha)014:1416: te / rong zom chen po'i t+ai ka las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:1417: sgo'i bsil khang rnams dang ldan par grags pas gzhal
NK014(pha)014:1418: med khang gi sgo thams cad spyir shes par bya
NK014(pha)014:1420: chos don gyi rnam bshad mdzad pa po dag gis kyang /
NK014(pha)014:1421: rta babs nang can mthong khung can du //
NK014(pha)014:1422: zhes gsungs pa'ang 'di la dgongs par mngon no //
NK014(pha)014:1423: de'ang zar tshags kyi snam bu sna 'phyang las 'phyang ba /
NK014(pha)014:1424: sna 'phyong ni gzhi ser po dkyil 'khor gyi pha gu dang mtshan nyid 'dra ba /
NK014(pha)014:1425: chun 'phyang ni gzhan las seng mgo'i snam bu zhes 'byung bas /
NK014(pha)014:1426: gzhi bar stong la seng mgo'i kha nas dpyangs pa'i
NK014(pha)014:1427: rin po che'i do shal dang do shal phyed pa
NK014(pha)014:1428: / shar bu ni dkyil 'khor gyi shar bu dang
NK014(pha)014:1429: mtshungs pa las 'dir gzhi sngon po'i steng du sgrigs
NK014(pha)014:1430: / pa yin no // de man gyi snam bu
NK014(pha)014:1431: bdun po de mdun ngos su phar bskum tshur 'phyar
NK014(pha)014:1432: / pa yin no // med pa'i phyir / mtshams
NK014(pha)014:1433: gcod kyi ri mo yod pa ma gtogs khad mnyam
NK014(pha)014:1434: / pa yin no // med pa'i phyir / la
NK014(pha)014:1435: / g.yas g.yon du 'phyar ba'i 'dod yon gyi cha
NK014(pha)014:1436: rnams pang leb srab mos dgab dgos pas /
NK014(pha)014:1439: sna 'phyong la 'og gzhi kha kheb gnyis ka dgos so //
NK014(pha)014:1440: shar bu'i snam bu'i steng du khyung mgo ni /
NK014(pha)014:1441: bya 'dab dang 'dra ba las zur bzhir khyung mgo'i
NK014(pha)014:1442: lkog ma nas zur dril dang bcas pa rta babs
NK014(pha)014:1443: 'og ma rnams las mdun du'ang 'phyar cha phran phyed
NK014(pha)014:1445: snam bu de rnams g.yas g.yon du /
NK014(pha)014:1446: gser gdung dang rta rkang ka rgyan dang khad mnyam la /
NK014(pha)014:1447: de nas chu sgrom gnyis cha phran gcig 'phyar /
NK014(pha)014:1452: de las khyung mgo gcig 'phyar ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:1453: de ltar rta babs 'god pa'i rim pa 'di ni /
NK014(pha)014:1455: 'bras bu'i yon tan kun rdzogs phyir //
NK014(pha)014:1456: rta rkang chu skyes rin chen sgrom //
NK014(pha)014:1457: sna 'phyang gzhi las za ra tshags //
NK014(pha)014:1458: rin chen sgril 'phyangs shar bu khyung //
NK014(pha)014:1459: rim bzhin dbyibs mdog mdzes par bya //
NK014(pha)014:1462: zhabs dang pad+ma rin chen snod //
NK014(pha)014:1463: sna 'phyangs las byung za ra tshags //
NK014(pha)014:1464: chun 'phyangs shar bu bya khyung mgo //
NK014(pha)014:1465: rim bzhin kha dog mdzes par bya //
NK014(pha)014:1477: rta babs gdung bzhi'i steng du'o //
NK014(pha)014:1479: 'di dag sngar drangs pa'i sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa'i lung dang yang mthun no //
NK014(pha)014:1482: zhabs dang ma chags za ra tshags //
NK014(pha)014:1484: sna tshogs khyung mgos rim par 'khrigs //
NK014(pha)014:1486: rgyud 'khrugs pa shing rta chen po'i slob dpon rnams kyi man ngag gis 'chad dgos pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:1487: 'od rim la sogs pa ltar lag tu blang na legs par snang bas de bzhin du byas so //
NK014(pha)014:1488: snam bu rnams ni mdun ngos su glang rgyab brkos
NK014(pha)014:1489: pa'i mig 'og ma dang nang gi bcu gcig rdo
NK014(pha)014:1490: rje'i d+r+wa mig khad mnyam du yod cing /
NK014(pha)014:1491: sgo khang gi gdung dang thog 'bubs kyang phyi nas mthong bas /
NK014(pha)014:1492: de la bsil khang gi nang rnams phyogs mdog can
NK014(pha)014:1493: yin pa'i de dang mthun pa'i tshon rtsis byugs nas
NK014(pha)014:1495: gdung de'i 'og ya phubs kyi pany+tsa re kh+aa'i mdun du bla re dbub /
NK014(pha)014:1496: de'i phyi mtshams sum phubs kyi bya 'dab kyi sna
NK014(pha)014:1497: las rin po che'i d+r+wa ba cung zad re 'phyang
NK014(pha)014:1499: glang rgyab kyi mig dbus ma'i nang du sgril 'phyang
NK014(pha)014:1500: gi snam bu'i d+r+wa ba mthong bas d+r+wa phyed zur
NK014(pha)014:1502: byed na chu srin gyi kha nas byung ba'i mu
NK014(pha)014:1503: tig gi do shal dang do shal phyed pa dril
NK014(pha)014:1504: bu rnga yab dang bcas pa bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:1506: steng ni glang dang skas rgyab sogs //
NK014(pha)014:1507: ji ltar mdzes pa'i tshul du bzhengs //
NK014(pha)014:1510: sh+r+aad+d+ha'i rta babs sgo tshad ma gcig ma'i snam bu
NK014(pha)014:1511: dang po la skabs su bshad pa shar bu dang
NK014(pha)014:1513: rta babs kyi shar bu dang de'i steng du glang
NK014(pha)014:1514: rgyab mtshon tsam byed pa yin 'dra gsungs na'ang gzhung
NK014(pha)014:1515: de nyid las / skas dang glang po rgyab 'dra dang //
NK014(pha)014:1517: ji ltar mdzes par bstan pa yin //
NK014(pha)014:1518: zhes de gnyis 'dam khar gsungs pa 'dra bas /
NK014(pha)014:1519: spyi ming bye brag la dgar te /
NK014(pha)014:1520: mig gsum ma la glang rgyab tu byas nas /
NK014(pha)014:1522: yang na skyogs po bdun pa dang dgu pa sogs
NK014(pha)014:1523: deng sang pu na ha rir 'bod pa 'di byas
NK014(pha)014:1524: pa'i tshe g.yas g.yon bar stong gi mun pa'i dbyibs
NK014(pha)014:1525: them skas kyi rim pa lta bu zhig 'ong ba
NK014(pha)014:1528: snga rabs kyi yo ga ba 'ga' zhig /
NK014(pha)014:1529: shar du glang po'i rgyab dang /
NK014(pha)014:1532: byang du skas kyi rnam par bya /
NK014(pha)014:1533: zhes zer ba'ang snang bas da dung dpyad par bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:1534: rgya phubs kyi dbus su chos 'khor gyi gdan pad+ma
NK014(pha)014:1535: dmar po rgya cha chung gnyis dang dpangs su gcig
NK014(pha)014:1536: / de'i steng du sman t+aika pas /
NK014(pha)014:1537: chos 'khor bcu gsum brtsegs mar bshad kyang /
NK014(pha)014:1539: 'khor lo sa yi khyad par yin //
NK014(pha)014:1540: zhes pa rtse mchod rten gyi dbyibs la dgongs kyi
NK014(pha)014:1541: 'dir de ltar bya dgos pa'i nges pa med pa
NK014(pha)014:1542: dang / thig chog tu cha chung gnyis pa'i dpangs las ma gsungs pa'i phyir mi mdzes pas /
NK014(pha)014:1543: 'dir gser gyi 'khor lo rgya cha chung gnyis pa
NK014(pha)014:1544: lnga cha phran dang ldan pa'i mu khyud can rtsibs
NK014(pha)014:1545: brgyad pa bslang ba'i khar gdugs dkar po dbub /
NK014(pha)014:1546: g.yas g.yon du mi ring bar gser las byas pa'i
NK014(pha)014:1547: ri dwags kyi gzugs pho ni rwa dang bcas pa
NK014(pha)014:1548: dang / mo ni rwa med pa rin po che'i rgyan gyis spras pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:1550: chos kyi 'khor lo cha gnyis te //
NK014(pha)014:1551: gdugs dang yu ba cha re'o //
NK014(pha)014:1552: zhes cha chen gcig la 'khor lo cha phran gnyis dang /
NK014(pha)014:1555: de ltar na'ang bka' brgyad zhi ba'i thig chog tu /
NK014(pha)014:1557: gdugs rnams cha phran bzhi pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:1559: bla ma rnams phyag len du'ang yod pa'i phyogs mdzad de /
NK014(pha)014:1560: de ltar na pad+ma yod pa'i khyad kyi gdugs kyi
NK014(pha)014:1561: yu ba cha phran gcig po 'khor lo'i phag tu
NK014(pha)014:1562: btang nas / cha phran gcig pa'i gdugs bya ba'am /
