NK014(pha)014:1564: gdugs cha phyed las yu ba phyed //
NK014(pha)014:1565: ces pa ltar cha phran phyed phyed du byed pa'am /
NK014(pha)014:1567: pad+ma'i dpangs cha phran gcig gi phyed rgya phubs kyi
NK014(pha)014:1568: lan kan phag tu 'gro bar byas nas ji tsam
NK014(pha)014:1569: song ba'i tshad kyi gdugs kyi yu ba mthong bar
NK014(pha)014:1571: chos kyi 'khor lo'i thad ka'i 'og bsil khang gi nang du cong dang /
NK014(pha)014:1574: dril bu rnams kyang 'dogs par bzhed do //
NK014(pha)014:1576: chos kyi 'khor lo gtso bo'i brda //
NK014(pha)014:1577: ri dwags 'khor gyi brda yin te //
NK014(pha)014:1578: cong ni nges don brda sgra yin //
NK014(pha)014:1579: gan+di drang don brda yin te //
NK014(pha)014:1580: rdor dril thabs dang shes rab brda //
NK014(pha)014:1582: de ltar rta babs kyi skor 'di la mkhas pa gzhan yang khang thog 'phang dmas pa'i skyon dang /
NK014(pha)014:1583: lcog gi mdzes cha las sgo mdun du rgyan med
NK014(pha)014:1584: pa mi mdzes par che bar 'dod pa dang rta
NK014(pha)014:1585: babs mdun du bslang ba'i sgo tshad gcig ma sogs
NK014(pha)014:1586: sgo'i har mi sgribs pa mthong nas /
NK014(pha)014:1587: sgom don gyi rta babs sgo tshad gsum mas khyab
NK014(pha)014:1588: pas gcig ma gsungs pa rnams bris cha kho nar
NK014(pha)014:1590: glang rgyab mig gsum ma rta babs kyi 'og tu
NK014(pha)014:1591: sgo'i rlung po sgribs byed kyi tshul du 'dod pa
NK014(pha)014:1592: sogs pheb ka ris kyi bshad pa sna tshogs byung
NK014(pha)014:1593: ba de dag / da phyin chad chu shing gi 'bras bu ltar snying po med par 'gyur zhing /
NK014(pha)014:1594: yang dag pa'i gzhung 'di la nges par 'brangs par 'gyur te /
NK014(pha)014:1595: bdag gi rje bla ma'i legs bshad 'di'i mthu las so //
NK014(pha)014:1598: rnga yab lhab lhub phreng ba yis //
NK014(pha)014:1599: nges par phyogs bcur 'khrigs par bya //
NK014(pha)014:1600: zhes gsungs pa ltar sngar so so'i skabs su smos pa rnams dang /
NK014(pha)014:1601: der ma zad bde 'dus rigs brgya'i sgrub thabs las /
NK014(pha)014:1602: ba dan 'phan dang rdo rje rin chen rgyal mtshan mdzes par bya /
NK014(pha)014:1604: snying po rol pa chen po'i rgyud las /
NK014(pha)014:1605: gdugs dang ba dan rgyal mtshan tshogs //
NK014(pha)014:1606: rdo rje rin chen mtshan pa dang //
NK014(pha)014:1608: gzhal yas khang dngos gzhi'i pu shu'i zur bzhi dang /
NK014(pha)014:1609: sgo'i bsil khang gi mdun gyi ka ba nang ma
NK014(pha)014:1610: gnyis kyi phyi mtshams kyi thad steng rnams su dar
NK014(pha)014:1611: lce'i sham bu dang bcas pa'i gdugs dkar po rdo
NK014(pha)014:1612: rje rin po che'i tog can /
NK014(pha)014:1613: yu ba cha chung phyed dang gsum yod pa re re ste /
NK014(pha)014:1614: gzhung gzhan las spre'u'i gzung bar bshad do //
NK014(pha)014:1615: thog gi pu shu'i kho ra khor yug dang /
NK014(pha)014:1616: rta babs kyi steng gi zur bzhi dang sgrom gyi
NK014(pha)014:1617: snam bu'i mtha' rnams su rin po che'i bum pa
NK014(pha)014:1618: la gnas pa'i rgyal mtshan dang ba dan sgreng ba'o
NK014(pha)014:1620: rin po che'i dbyug pa'i rtser tog gi gdan zlum
NK014(pha)014:1621: po'i steng 'og tu re kh+aa'i bang rim ci rigs
NK014(pha)014:1623: de'i steng gi dkyil du rin po che dang rdo
NK014(pha)014:1624: rje'i tog byas pa'i tog gi gdan dang dbyug pa'i
NK014(pha)014:1625: mtshams nas g.yas g.yon gyi phyogs su dril bu dang
NK014(pha)014:1626: bcas pa'i dar dpyangs sam 'phan ring btags pa rlung
NK014(pha)014:1627: gis bskyod pas sum 'khyog tu lding ba /
NK014(pha)014:1628: ba dan ni gzhan de dang 'dra ba la tog gi gdan mi dgos pa yin no //
NK014(pha)014:1629: gzhung gzhan las ni rgyal mtshan gyi tog srog chags kyi gzugs kyis byas pa 'dod pa'ang yod do //
NK014(pha)014:1630: gzhal yas khang dbus kyi rtse mo'i tog nas gser
NK014(pha)014:1631: gyi thi gu'i pu shu'i kha'i dbyug pa ring po
NK014(pha)014:1632: la bcings pa'i ba dan gyi mgul mtshams la dkris
NK014(pha)014:1633: nas rta babs kyi 'khor lo'i steng gi gdugs kyi
NK014(pha)014:1634: rtse mo'i bar du 'then pa la /
NK014(pha)014:1635: gser gyi dril bu rnga yab dang nyi zla'i rlung
NK014(pha)014:1636: bskyod can gyi tshar sgreng ba las sgra skad snyan
NK014(pha)014:1639: rta babs rnams kyi rtse mo la //
NK014(pha)014:1640: gser gyi dril bu 'bar ba dag /
NK014(pha)014:1641: dkon mchog gsum gyi sgra yang sgrogs //
NK014(pha)014:1643: bde 'dus zhi ba'i thig chog las /
NK014(pha)014:1644: ba dan dril bu legs par brgyan //
NK014(pha)014:1648: gzhal yas de yi sgo bzhi na //
NK014(pha)014:1649: glang chen rnams kyi mdzes par bya //
NK014(pha)014:1652: glang seng gnyis kyis mdzes par bya //
NK014(pha)014:1653: zhes pa'i phyi ma ltar na /
NK014(pha)014:1655: sgo bzhi yi ni logs dag tu //
NK014(pha)014:1656: glang chen dang ni seng ge bri //
NK014(pha)014:1657: zhes sgo logs la bri bar bshad cing /
NK014(pha)014:1659: phyi rol sgo ba glang seng dang //
NK014(pha)014:1663: sgo khang nang gi rgyan dgu ni //
NK014(pha)014:1664: rmang na nyon mongs zil gyis gnon //
NK014(pha)014:1665: glang dang seng ge ngang pa dang //
NK014(pha)014:1666: stobs dang mi 'jigs tshad med do //
NK014(pha)014:1667: sa le'i shing gi tshal yin na //
NK014(pha)014:1668: bar na las rnams so sor 'byed //
NK014(pha)014:1669: ri dwags mi dang srang kham dang //
NK014(pha)014:1670: g.yo dang 'byed dang stobs pa ste //
NK014(pha)014:1671: blon po rin po che bzhin no //
NK014(pha)014:1672: steng na sdug bsngal dang du len //
NK014(pha)014:1673: klu dang chu srin ga ru da //
NK014(pha)014:1674: ye shes thugs rje'i phrin las te //
NK014(pha)014:1675: khyung gi klu rgyal blang ba bzhin //
NK014(pha)014:1677: slob dpon chen po pad+mas mdzad pa'i gsang rdzogs ma h+aa'i sgom rim las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:1678: sgo khang mun nag grib sos brgyan pa la //
NK014(pha)014:1679: bya khyung chu srin klu phrug gsum //
NK014(pha)014:1680: dge sdig bya ra ri dwags shang shang gsum //
NK014(pha)014:1681: seng ge glang chen ngang pa gsum ste dgu pa tras sbrel ba /
NK014(pha)014:1682: zhes gsungs pas sgo khang nang gi sgo'i g.yas g.yon
NK014(pha)014:1683: du rim pa gsum du bgos pa'i smad du glang
NK014(pha)014:1684: seng ngang pa / bar du ri dwags sha ra b+han /
NK014(pha)014:1689: sgo'i steng gi dbus su bya khyung /
NK014(pha)014:1690: de dag pa tra ris sbrel zhing //
NK014(pha)014:1691: rgyab nas sa le'i ljon shing skye ba'i 'dab ma bar bar nas mthong ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:1693: dbang gi rtags bcu 'di ltar te //
NK014(pha)014:1694: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba dang //
NK014(pha)014:1695: go cha rgyal mtshan phyag rgya dang //
NK014(pha)014:1696: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
NK014(pha)014:1697: snying po lnga ni ye shes dang //
NK014(pha)014:1698: chos mos rdzu 'phrul smon lam dang //
NK014(pha)014:1699: skye las tshe dang longs spyod dang //
NK014(pha)014:1700: sems la dbang ba'i go rim bzhin //
NK014(pha)014:1701: zhes pa'i stong tshar rnams su dbu rgyan sogs rtags bcu yang 'god do //
NK014(pha)014:1702: sgo rgyan gyi rgyan 'di dag rgya bal du bris
NK014(pha)014:1703: pa'i thang sku 'ga' zhig la'ang de bzhin snang ngo
NK014(pha)014:1704: // zhes mkhas mchog bu ston rin po ches gsungs /
NK014(pha)014:1705: kha cig dbang gi rtags bcu logs su 'god mi dgos te /
NK014(pha)014:1706: dang po bzhi dang phyag rgya sgo ba la bartsi'o //
NK014(pha)014:1707: rgyal mtshan dang gdugs ni sgo khang steng na'onga /
NK014(pha)014:1708: bza' btung ni 'dod yon lha mos so //
NK014(pha)014:1709: bum pa snying po lngas gdab ni /
NK014(pha)014:1710: rta babs kyi snam bu rnams la'o //
NK014(pha)014:1711: zhes gsungs te brtags par bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:1713: rin chen bdun ni 'di ltar te //
NK014(pha)014:1714: dbang ni 'khor lo rin chen dang //
NK014(pha)014:1715: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen dang //
NK014(pha)014:1716: lha mo btsun mo rin chen dang //
NK014(pha)014:1717: sgo ba dmag dpon tshul dgu dang //
NK014(pha)014:1718: mngon shes blon po bya ra ba //
NK014(pha)014:1719: stobs bcu glang po rin chen dang //
NK014(pha)014:1720: rdzu 'phrul ri dwags rta yi tshul //
NK014(pha)014:1721: rdzas brgyad la ni 'di ltar te //
NK014(pha)014:1722: bdud 'joms mi nub rgyal mtshan dang //
NK014(pha)014:1723: thugs rje gdugs dang dpal be'u dang //
NK014(pha)014:1724: bdud rtsi bum pa mi bsnyel rta //
NK014(pha)014:1727: zhes gsungs pa'i rin chen bdun dang /
NK014(pha)014:1728: rdzas brgyad kyang gong ma dag logs su 'god mi dgos par bzhed de /
NK014(pha)014:1729: gsang rdzogs ma h+aa'i sgom rim las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:1730: rin chen bdun dang bkra shis brgyad //
NK014(pha)014:1731: dbang bcu de la don gyi rdzogs pas /
NK014(pha)014:1732: zhes gsungs pa'i dgongs pa yin no snyam mo //
NK014(pha)014:1733: 'on kyang gzhan du 'byung ba ltar bkod na'ang mi 'gal lam snyam ste /
NK014(pha)014:1734: de'i phyir spyi dang bstun na 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa ser po /
NK014(pha)014:1735: glang chen mche ba drug pa dkar po /
NK014(pha)014:1738: nor bu zur brgyad pa sngon po /
NK014(pha)014:1740: dmag dpon nag po rnams phyi rol dpag bsam shing la gnas par bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:1741: rdzas brgyad ni rta babs kyi ngos gnyis su re re 'god do //
NK014(pha)014:1742: shar du dpal be'u dang 'khor lo /
NK014(pha)014:1744: nub tu gdugs dang bum pa /
NK014(pha)014:1746: de dag ni slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang
NK014(pha)014:1747: bas chos don du gsungs pa'i sgo rgyan te ma
NK014(pha)014:1748: grub na / 'dir med du mi rung ba'i rgyan ni /
NK014(pha)014:1749: sgo nang gi rgyan glang seng tsam bri /
NK014(pha)014:1751: sgo'i g.yas g.yon gnyis na t+aa la'i ljon shing re re dang /
NK014(pha)014:1752: dpag bsam gyi ljon shing yang re re ste /
NK014(pha)014:1753: de rnams gser gyi thi gus sbrel ba la /
NK014(pha)014:1754: dril bu dang g.yer kha 'phyang ba /
NK014(pha)014:1755: shing de dag la khu byug sogs byas brgyan pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:1756: khrus rdzing khrus kyi lha mos mdzes pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:1757: phyogs bzhi na rin po che'i phung po 'od 'bar ba gnyis gnyis te brgyad kyis bskor ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:1758: de ltar yang rngam glog las /
NK014(pha)014:1759: sgo drung de dag re re na //
NK014(pha)014:1760: t+aa la'i ljon shing cong cong sbrel //
NK014(pha)014:1761: dri dang gzugs dang 'od dang ldan //
NK014(pha)014:1762: t+aa la'i skye shing de dag la //
NK014(pha)014:1763: khu byug la sogs bkra shis pa'i //
NK014(pha)014:1764: bya rnams snyan pa'i skad kyang sgrogs //
NK014(pha)014:1765: sgo drung de dag re re na //
NK014(pha)014:1766: khrus kyi rdzing bu dbyibs legs pa //
NK014(pha)014:1767: bro mchog yan lag brgyad ldan chu //
NK014(pha)014:1768: grangs med de dag re re na //
NK014(pha)014:1769: lha dang lha mo bsam mi khyab //
NK014(pha)014:1772: t+aa la'i ljon shing rang bzhin gnas //
NK014(pha)014:1773: dpag bsam shing gi rin chen 'bar //
NK014(pha)014:1774: yid bzhin rin chen brgyad kyis bskor //
NK014(pha)014:1777: bden pa gsum pa'i ngang las dus gsum du skye
NK014(pha)014:1778: ba med pa'i phyir t+aa la zung bzhis brgyan pa'o
NK014(pha)014:1779: // re ba skong phyir rin chen phung po brgyad kyis bskor ba ste /
NK014(pha)014:1782: sgo bzhi g.yas g.yon ljon shing dang //
NK014(pha)014:1783: dpag bsam shing zung cong cong sbrel //
NK014(pha)014:1784: dril bu g.yer kha theg chen sgrogs //
NK014(pha)014:1785: bkra shis bya snyan sgra sgrogs ldan //
NK014(pha)014:1786: yid bzhin rin chen brgyad bskor ba //
NK014(pha)014:1787: rin chen phung po bzhi gnyis ldan //
NK014(pha)014:1789: 'di dag bsgom bya tsam du ma zad nges par bri dgos te /
NK014(pha)014:1791: rin chen sa gzhi skye shing dang //
NK014(pha)014:1792: rdzing bu dril bu g.yer khas spras //
NK014(pha)014:1793: rtag tu bri zhing bsgom par bya //
NK014(pha)014:1796: 'khor gyi gtso bos yongs bskul ba'i //
NK014(pha)014:1797: mchog gsum lha sogs rnams mang po //
NK014(pha)014:1798: rgyan dang mchod pa ldan par bri //
NK014(pha)014:1801: lha chen phyogs skyong brgyad kyis bskor //
NK014(pha)014:1807: sogs khong nas phyogs skyong ba brgyad sogs lha chen po rnams kyang 'god par gsungs shing /
NK014(pha)014:1808: sgro phug pa'i dngos slob kha rag sro snying gi 'grel par /
NK014(pha)014:1809: thams cad du ni dbang bsgyur phyir //
NK014(pha)014:1810: 'jig rten lha chen rnams kyis bskor //
NK014(pha)014:1811: zhes pas gzhal yas khang gi phyi rol na ma h+aa de wa la sogs lha chen brgyad dang /
NK014(pha)014:1812: nor rgyal la sogs klu chen brgyad dang /
NK014(pha)014:1813: nyi ma la sogs gza' chen brgyad dang /
NK014(pha)014:1814: smin drug la sogs pa rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis bskor ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:1815: zhes lha klu gza' skar sogs kyang dgod par bzhed cing /
NK014(pha)014:1816: de rnams gang du 'god pa'i sa sngar bshad grub bo //
NK014(pha)014:1817: 'di dag sgyu 'phrul zhi dkyil gyi gzhal yas khang gi rnam bzhag che long tsam brjod pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:1818: 'di dag la dpags te khro dkyil khyams gnyis pa lta bu'i thog phub ni /
NK014(pha)014:1819: bar khyams phyi ma seng gdung ngam ka bas btegs
NK014(pha)014:1820: pa'i g.yab sgor gru bzhi pa'i tshul du phubs pa'i
NK014(pha)014:1821: khyams nang du / rin chen gar dgu stegs bu
NK014(pha)014:1822: gru bzhi pa dpangs cha phran bcu gcig pa la
NK014(pha)014:1823: gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor phyi ma'i phyed tshad kyi rtsig
NK014(pha)014:1824: pa sgo sgo khyud la sogs pa byas pa'i gzhal
NK014(pha)014:1825: yas khang nang ma phyi ma las cha chen gcig
NK014(pha)014:1826: tsam gyis phyi nas bltas na mtho ba /
NK014(pha)014:1827: yangs pa zhig byas pa'i thog 'bubs rim pa gsum
NK014(pha)014:1828: sogs zhi ba ltar las nang sgo la rta babs
NK014(pha)014:1829: med pa'i phyir / de 'degs byed ka ba sogs
NK014(pha)014:1830: kyang mi dgos pas sgo'i ya phubs kyi rtsig pa'i
NK014(pha)014:1831: steng bar 'khor mo pha gu sogs gzhal yas dngos
NK014(pha)014:1837: thod pa sna lnga sna gsum dang //
NK014(pha)014:1838: thod skam rtsig pa rim pa bzhin //
NK014(pha)014:1839: tshangs dang lha dbang la brten pa //
NK014(pha)014:1840: mchog chen brgyad ka yin par 'dod //
NK014(pha)014:1841: lhag ma rnams ni thog phubs te //
NK014(pha)014:1842: gza' brgyad nyi zla'i glo skar ldan //
NK014(pha)014:1843: sbrul dang thod pa'i phreng ba nyid //
NK014(pha)014:1844: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed rnam par spras //
NK014(pha)014:1845: phyi nang rgyu 'bras gdug pa dag /
NK014(pha)014:1846: 'dul phyir rta babs bzhir bshad do //
NK014(pha)014:1847: sor phreng thod pa'i phreng ba dang //
NK014(pha)014:1848: dbang po nyi zla'i phreng bas spras //
NK014(pha)014:1849: khro bo sha lnga bdud rtsi dang //
NK014(pha)014:1851: dur khrod sa gzhi khrag dang bcas //
NK014(pha)014:1852: skyes bu gsal zhing phyogs mtshams brgyan //
NK014(pha)014:1854: thod tshal brgyus pa dur khrod rlung //
NK014(pha)014:1856: zhing 'phan phyogs mtshams brgyad dang ldan //
NK014(pha)014:1857: lha chen thod pa sbubs steng na //
NK014(pha)014:1859: he ru ka yi dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK014(pha)014:1860: ma lus bri zhing bsgom par bya //
NK014(pha)014:1861: zhes gsungs pas gzhan rnams go sla la /
NK014(pha)014:1863: phyi ma thod pa sna lnga dang /
NK014(pha)014:1864: nang ma skam rlon rnying gsum gyis brtsigs shing /
NK014(pha)014:1865: khyams las gru chad stegs bu'i rnam par thod skam gyi rtsig pas 'phags pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:1868: de re re la snam phran brgyad brgyad do //
NK014(pha)014:1870: zhes pas phyi nang gi theg brgyad mtshon pa'i rgyu'i rta babs dang /
NK014(pha)014:1871: de'i yon tan rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu'i rta babs gnyis so //
NK014(pha)014:1872: 'dir dkyil 'khor nang ma stegs bu la gnas pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:1873: de la 'dzegs pa'i them skas kyang 'dzug dgos par mngon no //
NK014(pha)014:1874: de lta bus mtshon nas sgyu 'phrul bla ma las gsungs pa ltar /
NK014(pha)014:1875: spor ma'i sa spar te sgo brag rim pa gsum du bya ba 'am /
NK014(pha)014:1876: yang tshogs chen 'dus pa lta bu sgo sbrag shin
NK014(pha)014:1877: tu mang ba la'ang sbyar bas khang brtsegs mchod rten
NK014(pha)014:1878: gyi bang rim 'dra ba shin tu mdzes pa zhig
NK014(pha)014:1879: 'byung ngo // yang bka' brgyad lta bu gzhal yas
NK014(pha)014:1880: khang gcig gi nang du pho brang dgu rdzogs sogs
NK014(pha)014:1882: khyams cha phran gsum gyi cha g.yab gru bzhi pa'i
NK014(pha)014:1883: tshul du phubs pa'i gru chad dang khyams kyi mtshams
NK014(pha)014:1884: tshangs thig nas gru chad kyi mtha' thig bar cha
NK014(pha)014:1885: gsum du bgos pa'i sum cha nang ma'i phyi mtshams
NK014(pha)014:1886: su ka ba re re ste brgyad btsugs pa'i steng
NK014(pha)014:1887: du gdung ka ba gru bzhi pas bkab /
NK014(pha)014:1888: de'i khar tal bzhi mig mang ris su bris te 'bubs so //
NK014(pha)014:1889: 'dir bsgom bya la tal gdung bzhi'i 'og tu yod
NK014(pha)014:1890: pa'i gru bzhi pa de a long gru bzhi pa
NK014(pha)014:1891: lta bu yin pa'i phyir zur bzhir 'degs byed kyi
NK014(pha)014:1892: ka ba yin dgos gsung yang 'di lta bu'i bkod
NK014(pha)014:1893: pa bzo ba'i dus 'di ltar byas na brtan zhing
NK014(pha)014:1895: gsang rdzogs ma h+aa'i bsgom rim las /
NK014(pha)014:1896: nang ka bzhi zhing tram bzhi la byas pa /
NK014(pha)014:1898: rgyal sras sman lung pa chen pos phyag len du btab pa mthong bas kyang /
NK014(pha)014:1899: gdung bzhi mig mang ris phub pa'i dbus kyi bsnol mtshams su ka ba re btsugs 'dug ste /
NK014(pha)014:1900: gzhal yas khang gi bkod pa shin tu che ba
NK014(pha)014:1901: bzhengs pa la de lta bu nges par dgos so
NK014(pha)014:1902: // yang gsang rdzogs ma h+aa'i bsgom rim las /
NK014(pha)014:1903: chos sku kun la khyab brdal mtha' brgyad rang dag gi brdar /
NK014(pha)014:1904: bum pa sul brgyad pa bre dang bcas /
NK014(pha)014:1905: zhes gsungs pa ltar na shing brtsegs ji ltar rigs
NK014(pha)014:1906: pas btegs pa'i gdung brgyad phyogs bzhi zur bzhir btang
NK014(pha)014:1907: la phub ste / bum pa zur brgyad logs brgyad
NK014(pha)014:1908: pa zhig bya ste mchod rten gyi bya 'dab 'geb
NK014(pha)014:1909: la phub ste / pa dang / gdung zlum btang
NK014(pha)014:1910: ba sogs lag len la shin tu bde ba zhig
NK014(pha)014:1911: la phub ste / pa dang / byar yod do
NK014(pha)014:1912: // gzhan yang rta babs sgo tshad gsum ma lta
NK014(pha)014:1913: la phub ste / pa dang / byar yod do
NK014(pha)014:1914: // bu la / rtsig pa'i dpangs cha chen bzhi
NK014(pha)014:1915: dang sgo khang gi rtsig pa la cha chen gsum
NK014(pha)014:1917: rta babs sgo tshad gcig ma la rtsig dpangs cha chen gnyis dang cha phran gsum /
NK014(pha)014:1918: sgo phan chad de las cha phran gcig gis dma' ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:1919: 'bring tshad ni 'di nyid du sngar bshad pa ltar ro //
NK014(pha)014:1920: de ltar na rtsig dpangs mtho ba'i phyogs la rtsig pa rang la nang gi rgya phyed dpangs /
NK014(pha)014:1921: 'bring la gser gdung man chad la /
NK014(pha)014:1922: dma' ba la thog gi 'thug rngam man chad la rgya phyed dpangs yod do //
NK014(pha)014:1923: de bas na skabs thob brtsi dgos kyi /
NK014(pha)014:1924: phyogs gcig kho nar nges bzung byed pa la shes byed med cing /
NK014(pha)014:1926: gang ltar yang phyi dbyibs ni /
NK014(pha)014:1932: phyi dbyibs mchod rten mkhar thabs dang //
NK014(pha)014:1933: rgyal khab ri bo gur du 'dod //
NK014(pha)014:1936: dbyibs ni mchod rten ris mkhar thabs //
NK014(pha)014:1937: gur dang rgyal khab 'dra ba yin //
NK014(pha)014:1940: dang po mchod rten gyi dbyibs byed lugs la'ang dgongs pa mi mthun pa gnyis te /
NK014(pha)014:1941: snga rabs kyi bla ma phal che ba ni /
NK014(pha)014:1942: gzhal yas khang dngos gzhi'i pu shu man chad mchod rten gyi rmang lta bur byas la /
NK014(pha)014:1943: de'i steng du byang chen sogs mchod rten gyi dbyibs gang bde bya ba bzhed /
NK014(pha)014:1944: gsang rdzogs las gsungs pa ltar nyang ston chen po'i phyag len du btab pa'i lugs ni /
NK014(pha)014:1947: pho brang rnams phyi nas nang du rim par cha
NK014(pha)014:1948: chen gcig nas bzhi'i bar 'phags pa'i bang rim bzhi'i
NK014(pha)014:1949: rnam pa can gyi steng du /
NK014(pha)014:1952: bre sogs byas te byang chen rmang med pa lta bu'i phyogs bzhir /
NK014(pha)014:1953: rta babs bzhi yang ka ba cha chen gsum pas btegs nas /
NK014(pha)014:1954: sgo'i steng nas yar mchod rten gyi rnam par byas te /
NK014(pha)014:1955: phyi dbyibs mchod rten rtse lnga pa'i rnam par bzhed do //
NK014(pha)014:1957: kha cig steng khang gru bzhi pa la dgongs par 'chad pa mi rigs gsungs so //
NK014(pha)014:1959: bdud dpung 'joms pa'i dag par gsungs pa'i rdzong gi rnam pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:1961: de tsam las bya thabs zhib par ma gsungs na'ang /
NK014(pha)014:1962: 'os med kyi rigs pas 'di ltar grub ste /
NK014(pha)014:1963: 'jam dpal phyag rgya zil gnon las /
NK014(pha)014:1964: e yi pho brang zla gam gsum thod pa'i mkhar
NK014(pha)014:1965: bzhi 'khor lo brgyad lcags mkhar bcu gnyis bar khyams
NK014(pha)014:1966: bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs brgyad dang ldan 'obs chen
NK014(pha)014:1967: bcu drug rdo rje'i gur byas pa med par lhun
NK014(pha)014:1968: gyis grub bshig pa med par ngang gi stong zhes
NK014(pha)014:1969: gsungs pas / dkyil 'khor gyi mthar 'obs bcu drug dang /
NK014(pha)014:1970: de bsrung mi 'obs bsrung chen po bcu drug sogs gsungs pas /
NK014(pha)014:1971: rdzong gi sgra durga zhes pas bgrod dka' ba'i don yin pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:1973: de las gzhan du rdzong gi rnam pa bzo tshul 'tshol dgos na ha cang thal lo //
NK014(pha)014:1974: gsum pa rgyal khab kyi rnam pa ni /
NK014(pha)014:1975: rgya gar gyi rgyal po'i khab kyi khang bzang gi rnam pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:1976: rgya phub 'jig rten gyi lugs dang mthun par byas pa'i khang pa brtsegs pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:1977: bzhi pa gur gyi rnam pa ni /
NK014(pha)014:1978: dbus mtho ba'i phur bu zlum po rgya gur rnam pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:1979: dbus gdung zlum la btsugs nas 'bubs tshul bum pa zlum po dang gnad gcig go //
NK014(pha)014:1980: phyi dbyibs ji ltar byed kyang rtse mor rdo rje
NK014(pha)014:1981: rin po che'i tog ni nges par bya dgos te
NK014(pha)014:1982: / thams cad bshad pa mi langs pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:1985: rgyud sde gong 'og rnams nas dkyil 'khor bkod pa
NK014(pha)014:1986: gcig tu ma nges pa du ma zhig 'byung ste
NK014(pha)014:1987: / so so'i rgyud 'grel sgrub thabs dang /
NK014(pha)014:1988: rdo rje slob dpon gyi gsung ngag las sogs dgos pa nyid do //
NK014(pha)014:1989: rgyal ba'i pho brang nyams dga' bar //
NK014(pha)014:1990: rgyal ba nyid kyis gsungs pa bzhin //
NK014(pha)014:1991: rgyal sras rnams kyis bkral ba'i don //
NK014(pha)014:1992: rgyal mchog gter chen chos kyi rje'i //
NK014(pha)014:1993: gsung las cung zad zin pa rnams //
NK014(pha)014:1995: d+aa ri dra ba de yis sbyar //
NK014(pha)014:1996: nyes kun mkhas la bzod par gsol //
NK014(pha)014:1997: legs bshad gang mchis dge ba des //
NK014(pha)014:1998: rje btsun bla ma'i zhabs brtan cing //
NK014(pha)014:1999: mkha' khyab 'gro kun phyam gcig par //
NK014(pha)014:2000: rdo rje sems dpa' nyid gyur cig //
NK014(pha)014:2001: ces khro bo'i lo nag pa zla ba'i mar ngo'i
NK014(pha)014:2002: dus tshes bcu'i nyin o rgyan smin grol gling gi
NK014(pha)014:2003: chos grwar sug bris su sbyar ba'o //
NK014(pha)014:2007: // // ma h+aa yo ga'i dbang thams cad kyi thog mthar 'gro ba'i rgyug byang lhan thabs bzhugs /
NK014(pha)014:2008: bla ma dang dbyer ma mchis pa dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)014:2009: lhan skyes bde chen rig pa'i rdo rje yis //
NK014(pha)014:2010: log rtog bdag lta'i ri bo kun 'joms pa'i //
NK014(pha)014:2011: he ru ka dpal bla ma la btud de //
NK014(pha)014:2012: smin byed dbang gi mtshams sbyor 'dir gsal bya //
NK014(pha)014:2013: de yang snga 'gyur rnying ma bka' ma'i phyogs theg pa rim pa dgu'i /
NK014(pha)014:2014: phrin las kyi cho ga mtha' dag phyogs gcig tu bsdus nas gtan la phab pa las /
NK014(pha)014:2015: 'dir de nyid kyi bye brag rnal 'byor bla med
NK014(pha)014:2016: kyi nang tshan ma h+aa yo ga'i dbang thams cad
NK014(pha)014:2017: kyi thog mtha' sogs su sbyor rgyu'ii lhan thabs rgyug
NK014(pha)014:2019: thog mar dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga dang dbang sgrub
NK014(pha)014:2020: kyi bya ba rnams bdag 'jug gnang ba nod pa'i
NK014(pha)014:2021: mthar thug pa grub nas slob bu rnams sgrub khang
NK014(pha)014:2024: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyis ni //
NK014(pha)014:2025: lha rnams kyis ni khrus gsol ltar //
NK014(pha)014:2026: lha yi chu ni dag pa yis //
NK014(pha)014:2027: de bzhin bdag gis khrus bagyi'o //
NK014(pha)014:2028: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka te sa ma ya sh+r+ai ye h+aum /
NK014(pha)014:2031: lta bu rang rang gi las sngags dang /
NK014(pha)014:2032: yi ge brgya pa brjod bzhin las kyi rdo rjes
NK014(pha)014:2033: las bum thogs te dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rol du
NK014(pha)014:2034: phyin nas slob bu rnams la khrus bya /
NK014(pha)014:2035: de nas slob bu rnams kyis phyag byas nas gral du 'khod pa dang bstun /
NK014(pha)014:2036: slob dpon gyis sngon gtor la /
NK014(pha)014:2037: las sngags kyis bum chu 'thor zhing bsang /
NK014(pha)014:2038: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ha sarba d+harmah swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho&aham /
NK014(pha)014:2040: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i snod
NK014(pha)014:2041: yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du gtor ma kha
NK014(pha)014:2042: dog dri ro nus pa phun sum tshogs par bsam
NK014(pha)014:2044: sarba b+h+au ta a kar+sha ya dzahs mgron rnams bkug /
NK014(pha)014:2045: sarba big+h+n+aam na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi
NK014(pha)014:2046: shwa mu khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ut+ga te s+pha ra
NK014(pha)014:2047: na i mam ga ga na kham grih+ne dam ba
NK014(pha)014:2049: zhes lan gsum gyis bsngosa la /
NK014(pha)014:2050: na mo dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)014:2051: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2052: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2053: chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bden pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2054: bden pa chen po'i byin gyi rlabs kyis slob ma
NK014(pha)014:2055: lhag gnas kyi chos rnams sgrub pa la bar du
NK014(pha)014:2056: gcod par byed pa'i 'byung po gdon bgegs kyi tshogs
NK014(pha)014:2057: thams cad 'dir ma gnas par gzhan du 'gro bar
NK014(pha)014:2058: gyis shig / ces pa dang dbang dngos gzhi'i skabs su /
NK014(pha)014:2059: bden pa chen po'i byin gyi rlabs kyis deng 'dir
NK014(pha)014:2060: skal ldan gyi slob bu 'di rnams la gsang sngags
NK014(pha)014:2061: rdo rje theg pa'i lam gyi 'jug sgo dang po
NK014(pha)014:2062: smin byed kyi dbang bskur ba la bar du gcod
NK014(pha)014:2063: par byed pa'i tshogs zhes 'jug bsgyur /
NK014(pha)014:2065: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u phata /
NK014(pha)014:2066: ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK014(pha)014:2067: zhes pa lta bu cho ga rang rang gi gtso
NK014(pha)014:2068: bo yab yum gyi bskyed sngags brjod pas lha snang
NK014(pha)014:2069: gsal btab la / h'u h'u h'u /
NK014(pha)014:2070: bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata phata /
NK014(pha)014:2071: ha la ha la ha la h+aum /
NK014(pha)014:2072: zhes brjod pas yab yum mnyam par rol pa'i sbyor
NK014(pha)014:2073: mtshams nas byang chub sems kyi sprin las khro bo
NK014(pha)014:2074: 'chol ba'i tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pa phyir 'phros
NK014(pha)014:2075: te bdud bgegs log par 'dren pa thams cad tshar
NK014(pha)014:2079: grih+na p+aa ya grih+na p+aa ya h+aum /
NK014(pha)014:2080: +aa na ya hoh b+ha ga wan bid+y+aa r+aa dza h+aum phata /
NK014(pha)014:2081: sogs drag sngags bzla zhing thun gyis brabs te spos
NK014(pha)014:2082: rol dang bcas mtshams rngams kyis bgegs rnams phyir bskrad
NK014(pha)014:2085: zhes brjod pas phyogs mtshams steng 'og thams cad rdo
NK014(pha)014:2086: rje srung ba'i ra ba d+r+wa ba gur bla bre
NK014(pha)014:2088: dus mtha'i rlung nag rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs 'khrugs pa'i
NK014(pha)014:2089: ra ba sum rim gyis phyogs kun khyab pas mtshams
NK014(pha)014:2090: bcad par bsam la srung 'khor gsal btab /
NK014(pha)014:2091: de nas las kyi rdo rjes me tog bkram bsdu bya zhing /
NK014(pha)014:2093: 'o nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad
NK014(pha)014:2094: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK014(pha)014:2095: rgyas kyi go 'phang la 'god par bya /
NK014(pha)014:2096: de'i ched du gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lam
NK014(pha)014:2097: gyi 'jug sgo dang po mngon par dbang bskur ba'i
NK014(pha)014:2098: sbyor ba slob ma lhag gnas kyi chos rnams zhus
NK014(pha)014:2099: nas smin grol lam gyi dngos gzhi la'ang rim pa
NK014(pha)014:2100: bzhin du bslab par bagyi'o snyam pas byang chub mchog
NK014(pha)014:2102: chos gsan pa'i kun tu spyod pa yang skyes rabs las /
NK014(pha)014:2103: rab tu dma' ba'i stan la 'dug /
NK014(pha)014:2104: dul ba'i dpal ni rnam par bskyed //
NK014(pha)014:2105: dga' dang ldan pa'i mig gis blta //
NK014(pha)014:2106: tshig gi bdud rtsi 'thung ba bzhin //
NK014(pha)014:2109: rtog pa thams cad legs par bsdus nas ni //
NK014(pha)014:2110: shin tu bsam pa bzang po ldan pas nyon //
NK014(pha)014:2111: brjed ngas blo la rdo rje sems dpa' sogs //
NK014(pha)014:2112: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyis byin mi rlob //
NK014(pha)014:2114: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la gus pa dang ldan pas
NK014(pha)014:2115: sgo gsum legs par bsdams te gzhan du ma yengs
NK014(pha)014:2116: pa'i sgo nas gsan par zhu 'tshal /
NK014(pha)014:2117: de yang 'o skol gyi ston pa yang dag par
NK014(pha)014:2118: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thabs mkhas la thugs rje chen
NK014(pha)014:2119: po mnga' ba de nyid kyis /
NK014(pha)014:2120: sems can rnams kyi bsam pa dang //
NK014(pha)014:2122: skal pa'i khyad par dang rjes su mthun pa'i chos
NK014(pha)014:2123: kyi bdud rtsi bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig bstan
NK014(pha)014:2124: pa thams cad kyang bsdu na theg pa che chung
NK014(pha)014:2127: sangs rgyas pa la bzhi pa dang //
NK014(pha)014:2128: lnga pa thub pa'i dgongs pa min //
NK014(pha)014:2133: theg pa gsum du rnam grol gyi theg pa thams
NK014(pha)014:2134: cad 'dus pas theg pa bzhi pa med mod kyang
NK014(pha)014:2135: / gsum po'i nang gses kyi dbye ba la brten
NK014(pha)014:2136: pa'i theg pa'i rnam grangs ni mang du 'byung ba
NK014(pha)014:2137: / mi 'gal te / lang kar gshegs pa las /
NK014(pha)014:2138: theg pa rnam pa mang bshad pa //
NK014(pha)014:2139: sems can rnams ni drangs pa'i phyir //
NK014(pha)014:2140: theg pa tha dad ngas bshad de //
NK014(pha)014:2141: theg pa gcig tu'ang ngas bstan to //
NK014(pha)014:2142: ji srid sems ni 'jug pa'i bar //
NK014(pha)014:2143: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK014(pha)014:2145: des na spyir mngon mtho'i theg pa gnyis /
NK014(pha)014:2146: nges par legs pa'i theg pa gsum dang lngar mdo sde las gsungs te /
NK014(pha)014:2148: lha yi theg dang tshangs pa'i theg /
NK014(pha)014:2149: de bzhin du ni nyan thos dang //
NK014(pha)014:2150: de bzhin gshegs dang rang rgyal gyi //
NK014(pha)014:2151: theg pa tha dad ngas bshad do //
NK014(pha)014:2153: yang mngon mtho'i theg pa gnyis gcig tu bsdus //
NK014(pha)014:2154: nges legs kyi de bzhin gshegs pa'i theg pa la
NK014(pha)014:2155: byang sems dang sngags gnyis su phyes nas lngar bshad
NK014(pha)014:2156: pa'ang yod de / gsang snying las /
NK014(pha)014:2157: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK014(pha)014:2158: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK014(pha)014:2160: de la mngon mtho'i theg pa ni /
NK014(pha)014:2161: las 'bras la yid ches pa'i sgo nas dge mi
NK014(pha)014:2162: dge'i blang dor ma nor bar spyad pas mi dang
NK014(pha)014:2163: 'dod lha'i go 'phang thob nus pa de'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:2165: lha'i theg pa zhes gsungs pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2166: de'i steng du 'jig rten pa'i bsam gtan dang gzugs
NK014(pha)014:2167: med kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa ni 'dod nyon
NK014(pha)014:2168: gyis gtsang bas tshangs pa'i theg pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:2169: de gnyis 'jig rten pa'i theg pa yin pas //
NK014(pha)014:2170: 'khor ba las 'phags par mi nus pa'i phyir /
NK014(pha)014:2172: theg pa 'di ni mkha' 'dra gzhal med khang chen te /
NK014(pha)014:2173: dga' bskyed bde ba mngon par thob byed theg pa'i mchog /
NK014(pha)014:2174: de gang zhon nas sems can thams cad mya ngan 'da' //
NK014(pha)014:2175: zhes pa las gzhan du gyur pas na theg pa dngos ma yin mod kyi /
NK014(pha)014:2176: de lta na'ang yang dag pa'i lta ba dang ldan pas dge bcu'i las lam la spyod pa ni /
NK014(pha)014:2177: rnam grol gyi theg pa thams cad kyi gazhi'am sngon
NK014(pha)014:2178: du 'gro ba yin pas lam stegs su 'gyur te
NK014(pha)014:2180: dge ba bcu las brtsams nas ni //
NK014(pha)014:2181: de yis chos ni rab tu byed //
NK014(pha)014:2183: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim du /
NK014(pha)014:2184: gzhi yi theg pa dang por zhog /
NK014(pha)014:2186: rin chen phreng ba las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:2187: mi yi chos lugs legs spyad na //
NK014(pha)014:2188: lha yul bgrod pa thag mi ring //
NK014(pha)014:2189: lha dang mi yi them skas la //
NK014(pha)014:2191: ces pa ltar mngon mtho'i them skas la 'dzegs nas bgrod bya'i gnas /
NK014(pha)014:2192: nges legs sam rnam par grol ba'i theg pa de
NK014(pha)014:2193: la'ang snga 'gyur rang skad kyi dbang du byas nas
NK014(pha)014:2194: / spyi mdo dgongs pa 'dus pa las /
NK014(pha)014:2195: lang ka'i bdag po gzhan yang gang //
NK014(pha)014:2196: don dam nges pa'i theg pa ni //
NK014(pha)014:2197: gsum du nges par bstan pa ste //
NK014(pha)014:2199: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:2200: zhes gsum du snang ba las /
NK014(pha)014:2201: re re la'ang gsum gsum du phye bas theg pa dgur 'gyur te /
NK014(pha)014:2202: kun 'byung 'dren pa'i theg pa ni nyan thos /
NK014(pha)014:2204: byang sems te mtshan nyid sde gsum dang /
NK014(pha)014:2205: dka' thub rigs byed kyi theg pa ni kri ya /
NK014(pha)014:2207: yo ga ste phyi rgyud sde gsum dang /
NK014(pha)014:2208: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa ni rgyud ma h+aa yo ga /
NK014(pha)014:2210: man ngag a ti yo ga ste nang rgyud sde gsum rnams su dbyer yod cing /
NK014(pha)014:2211: gsum mam dgur phye ba de yang bsdu na /
NK014(pha)014:2213: theg pa rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK014(pha)014:2214: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa dang //
NK014(pha)014:2217: rgyu pha rol tu phyin pa'i theg pa dang //
NK014(pha)014:2218: 'bras bu sngags kyi theg pa gnyis su 'du zhing /
NK014(pha)014:2219: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
NK014(pha)014:2220: sngags dang sbyor ba gtso bor ston pa dang mi ston pa'i khyad par ste /
NK014(pha)014:2222: mdo dang sngags kyi khyad par ni //
NK014(pha)014:2223: cho ga'i bya ba yod med yin //
NK014(pha)014:2224: zhes pa'ang don 'di la dgongs par snang ngo //
NK014(pha)014:2225: 'o na pha rol tu phyin pa'i tshul las /
NK014(pha)014:2226: sngags kyi tshul gang gis khyad par du 'phags snyam na /
NK014(pha)014:2227: don gsum gyis mdo las sngags mchog tu gyur pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:2231: thabs la mkhas pa'i khyad par ro //
NK014(pha)014:2233: phar phyin theg pa'i rang lam gyi byang chub thob pa la bskal pa grangs med gsum thogs mod /
NK014(pha)014:2235: kri yas mi tshe bdun nam bskal pa brgyad /
NK014(pha)014:2236: u pa yas mi tshe lnga'am bskal pa gcig gam gsum /
NK014(pha)014:2237: yo gas tshe lo brgya pa'i mi'i skye ba gsum mam bcu drug /
NK014(pha)014:2238: bla med kyis skye ba 'adi'am bar dor byang chub thob par gsungs shing /
NK014(pha)014:2239: de ltar myur ba'i rgyu yang /
NK014(pha)014:2241: cho ga'i khyad par gyis lha rnams dngos su mchod pa len pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2242: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyang
NK014(pha)014:2243: bla ma'i sku la zhugs nas sgrub pa po'i mchod
NK014(pha)014:2244: pa len pa la sogs pas yongs su spyad pa
NK014(pha)014:2245: las byung ba'i bsod nams yod pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2246: sngags dang phyag rgya'i mthus chu thigs re yang g+aang+ga'i
NK014(pha)014:2247: rdul snyed du 'phel bas de snyed kyi bsod nams
NK014(pha)014:2248: 'byung ba dang / ma dag pa'i snang ba 'gog
NK014(pha)014:2249: pa'i zhing sbyang ba'i ting nge 'dzin las dang po
NK014(pha)014:2250: pa'i dus nas kyang mngon du byed nus pa dang
NK014(pha)014:2251: 'byung ba dang / / sngags dang phyag rgya dang
NK014(pha)014:2252: ting nge 'dzin gyi khyad par re res kyang sems
NK014(pha)014:2253: can mtha' yas pa smin pa'i rgyu khyad par can
NK014(pha)014:2254: byed nus pa 'di dag sngags kyi theg pa la
NK014(pha)014:2255: zhugs tsam nyid nas yod pa'i rgyus myur ba yin
NK014(pha)014:2256: 'byung ba dang / / no // gnyis pa bde ba ni /
NK014(pha)014:2257: lus sems la tshor ba rtsub mo med pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:2258: de'i rgyu yang 'di las skal ba drug ldan gyi lus kyang tshegs med par grub pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2259: rdzu 'phrul dang ting nge 'dzin mang po thob pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2260: sngags kyi mthus de bzhin gshegs pa rnams mngon du
NK014(pha)014:2261: bzhugs shing 'gro ba'i bsam pa thams cad sgrub nus
NK014(pha)014:2262: pa'i rgyus bde ba yin no //
NK014(pha)014:2263: gsum pa thabs la mkhas pa ni /
NK014(pha)014:2264: rig pa 'dzin pa rnams dang tshul khrims mnyam pas lha dgyes pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2265: spyod yul khyad par can dang 'brel ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK014(pha)014:2266: shes rab rmad du byung bas snod bcud dag mnyam chen por gtan la pheb pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2267: spyod yul thams cad du lha dang sngags kyi thabs
NK014(pha)014:2268: la 'jug nus pas na thabs la mkhas pa yin
NK014(pha)014:2269: no // der ma zad pha rol tu phyin pa'i
NK014(pha)014:2270: rang lam gyis grangs med gsum du tshogs bsags pas
NK014(pha)014:2271: sa bcu pa'i byang chub sems dpa' sangs rgyas kyi
NK014(pha)014:2272: rgyal tshab chen po'i go 'phang las lhag pa thob
NK014(pha)014:2273: no // mi nus kyang / skabs der sngags kyi
NK014(pha)014:2274: theg pa la zhugs nas rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob
NK014(pha)014:2275: no // mi nus kyang / dgos pas na /
NK014(pha)014:2276: sngags kyi theg pa ni bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam
NK014(pha)014:2278: mthar thug gi theg pa gcig nyid du nges pas kyang 'phags te /
NK014(pha)014:2280: theg pa dpag med bstan pa yang //
NK014(pha)014:2281: ji ltar mos pa tha dad pas //
NK014(pha)014:2282: 'khrid par bya ba'i thabs su zad //
NK014(pha)014:2283: rdo rje theg pa nyid las med //
NK014(pha)014:2286: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK014(pha)014:2287: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK014(pha)014:2290: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK014(pha)014:2291: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab ltar //
NK014(pha)014:2292: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK014(pha)014:2293: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK014(pha)014:2295: 'o na gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa nyid sde snod gsum gang du 'du zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:2296: dgongs pa mi mthun pa mang ste /
NK014(pha)014:2297: gang dag mngon pa'i sde snod la phyi nang gnyis las sngags ni nang gi mngon pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:2299: zab mo'i don mdor bsdus te ston pas na mdo sde'o //
NK014(pha)014:2301: rang lugs ni rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod ces
NK014(pha)014:2302: sde snod gsum las logs par rkang thub pa gcig
NK014(pha)014:2303: tu byas te / sde snod bzhi par bzhag na legs par mngon no //
NK014(pha)014:2305: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK014(pha)014:2306: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK014(pha)014:2307: 'dul ba'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2308: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK014(pha)014:2309: mdo sde'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2310: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni /
NK014(pha)014:2311: mngon pa'i sde snod nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2312: thams cad 'dul ba'i gnyen por gsungs pa ni //
NK014(pha)014:2313: sde snod bzhi pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2315: dpung bzang gis zhus pa las kyang /
NK014(pha)014:2316: bye ba phrag gsum dang ni 'bum phrag lnga //
NK014(pha)014:2317: rig 'dzin sde snod du ni rgyal bas gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2319: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad pa'i rnam 'joms kyi gzungs 'grel las /
NK014(pha)014:2320: sangs rgyas mchog gis chos gsungs pa //
NK014(pha)014:2321: 'dul ba mdo sde mngon pa dang //
NK014(pha)014:2322: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde bzhir gnas //
NK014(pha)014:2324: rdo rje theg pa'i sde snod dang //
NK014(pha)014:2325: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod dang //
NK014(pha)014:2328: chos 'di pa rnams kyi rgyud ces pa rnams ming gi rnam grangs so //
NK014(pha)014:2329: de las sngags kyi mtshan gzhi ni /
NK014(pha)014:2330: sbyang gzhi dbyings rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2331: de la brten pa'i chos sbyang bya sbyong byed dang bcas pa thams cad yin zhing /
NK014(pha)014:2332: de yang sbyang gzhi la brten pa'i sbyang bya glo bur gyi dri ma rnams /
NK014(pha)014:2333: dbang gis rgyud smin par byas nas //
NK014(pha)014:2334: de dang 'brel ba'i rjes su lam bsgom pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2335: des bral thob kyi yon tan lam gyi char gtogs pa rnams sbyong byed yin la /
NK014(pha)014:2336: de ltar sbyangs pas dbyings la sgrib byed kyi dri ma phra rags thams cad dag nas /
NK014(pha)014:2337: gzhi'i yon tan ji lta ba bzhin mngon du gyur pa na 'bras bu ste /
NK014(pha)014:2340: dbyings la bral ba dag thob 'bras //
NK014(pha)014:2341: gsang sngags rnam pa bzhir bshad de //
NK014(pha)014:2344: chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2345: rjod byed thugs rdo rje'i gsang ba 'khor dang bcas pa ste /
NK014(pha)014:2347: sngags rnams kun gyi mtshan nyid ni //
NK014(pha)014:2348: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs yin te //
NK014(pha)014:2349: chos kyi snying po sgrub byed pas //
NK014(pha)014:2350: chos kyi dbyings dang yang dag ldan //
NK014(pha)014:2353: man+t+ra zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK014(pha)014:2354: yid shes bde myur du skyob pas na sngags te /
NK014(pha)014:2355: gsang 'dus kyi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK014(pha)014:2356: yid de man zhes bya bar bshad //
NK014(pha)014:2357: tra ni skyob par byed pa'i don //
NK014(pha)014:2359: gsang sngags kyi dbye ba ni /
NK014(pha)014:2360: gsar rnying thun mong gi bzhed pa'i dbang du byas na bzhir 'gyur te /
NK014(pha)014:2361: rdo rje snying po bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK014(pha)014:2362: bde bar gshegs pas dgongs pa'i rgyud //
NK014(pha)014:2363: rnam par bzhi ru yang dag bshad //
NK014(pha)014:2364: bya spyod rnal 'byor bla med do //
NK014(pha)014:2366: de yang bzhir 'byed pa'i rgyu mtshan ni lnga las /
NK014(pha)014:2367: dang po mi rigs bzhi yi spyod pa la dgongs nas /
NK014(pha)014:2368: de 'dul ba'i phyir bzhir gsungs te /
NK014(pha)014:2369: dur khrod rgyan gyi rgyud las /
NK014(pha)014:2370: bram ze rgyal rigs rje rigs dang //
NK014(pha)014:2371: dmang rigs gdol pa 'dul don du //
NK014(pha)014:2372: rgyud ni rnam pa bzhir gsungs te //
NK014(pha)014:2373: bya spyod rnal 'byor bla med do //
NK014(pha)014:2375: gnyis pa gang zag gi blo rigs bzhi la dgongs nas kyang bzhir gsungs te /
NK014(pha)014:2377: sems can dman la bya ba'i rgyud //
NK014(pha)014:2378: de lhag rnams la spyod pa'i rgyud //
NK014(pha)014:2379: sems can mchog la rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK014(pha)014:2380: de lhag rnams la bla med rgyud //
NK014(pha)014:2382: gsum pa rdzogs ldan la sogs pa'i dus bzhi la dgongs nas kyang bzhir gsungs te /
NK014(pha)014:2383: dpal phreng ba dam pa'i rgyud las /
NK014(pha)014:2384: gsang sngags byung tshul rnam bzhi ste //
NK014(pha)014:2385: bskal pa rdzogs ldan gsum ldan gnyis //
NK014(pha)014:2386: rtsod dus rgyud kyang rim bzhin du //
NK014(pha)014:2387: gdul bya'i ngo la snang ba yin //
NK014(pha)014:2389: bzhi pa sbyang gzhir 'dod chags kyi 'jug tshul bzhi la dgongs nas kyang bzhir gsungs te /
NK014(pha)014:2391: bltas dang dgod dang lag bcang dang //
NK014(pha)014:2392: 'khyud dang gnyis sprad la sogs pas //
NK014(pha)014:2393: rgyud kyang rnam pa bzhir gsungs so //
NK014(pha)014:2395: lnga pa lha bzhi'i rjes su 'jug pa'i phyin ci
NK014(pha)014:2396: log bzhi drangs pa la dgongs nas kyang bzhir gsungs
NK014(pha)014:2397: te / gti mug can tshangs pa gtsang sbra chos
NK014(pha)014:2398: su smra ba rjes su 'dzin pa'i phyir bya ba'i
NK014(pha)014:2399: te / rgyud / zhe sdang can khyab 'jug 'tshe
NK014(pha)014:2400: ba chos su smra ba rjes su 'dzin pa'i phyir
NK014(pha)014:2401: te / rgyud / spyod rgyud dang / nga rgyal
NK014(pha)014:2402: can brgya byin 'byor pa chos su smra ba rjes
NK014(pha)014:2404: 'dod chags can dbang phyug 'dod chags chos su smra
NK014(pha)014:2405: ba rjes su 'dzin pa'i phyir rnal 'byor bla na
NK014(pha)014:2406: med pa'i rgyud gsungs pa yin te /
NK014(pha)014:2407: de ltar rgyud sde bzhi las 'dir gsang sngags bla med 'chad pa skabs su bab pa yin /
NK014(pha)014:2408: de la yang rgyud ma h+aa yo ga lung a
NK014(pha)014:2409: nu yo ga man ngag a ti yo ga ste
NK014(pha)014:2411: dang po ma h+aa yo ga la nang gses tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad du grags pa las 'di ni /
NK014(pha)014:2413: dngos gzhi'i nyin me tog bkye bsdu'i mtshams nas gzhung
NK014(pha)014:2414: rang rang gi dngos gzhi'i chos bshad la 'jug par
NK014(pha)014:2415: bya ste / de yang rgyas par spro na dbang
NK014(pha)014:2416: bshad so so'i rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud
NK014(pha)014:2419: 'di ni rnal 'byor bla na med pa ste de la'ang dbye na /
NK014(pha)014:2420: gangs can gyi ljongs 'dir gsang sngags gsar rnying gi lugs srol gnyis byung /
NK014(pha)014:2421: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
NK014(pha)014:2422: lo ts+aa ba rin chen bzang po ma byon gong du 'gyur ba'i mdo rgyud rnams snga 'gyur dang /
NK014(pha)014:2423: de phyin 'gyur ba rnams gsang sngags gsar ma yin zhes bzhed de /
NK014(pha)014:2424: gtso che ba'i dbang du byas nas gsungs pa yin /
NK014(pha)014:2425: de ltar gsar rnying gnyis las /
NK014(pha)014:2426: 'dir gsar ma las khyad par du gyur pa gsang sngags rnying ma yin /
NK014(pha)014:2427: de yang gang gis khyad par du gyur zhe na /
NK014(pha)014:2428: lo ts+aa ba chen po rong zom chos kyi bzang po'i zhal snga nas /
NK014(pha)014:2429: gsang sngags rnying ma ba rnams la gsar ma las khyad par du 'phags pa'i che ba drug yod /
NK014(pha)014:2431: dang po spyan 'dren pa po yon bdag gi che ba ni /
NK014(pha)014:2432: snga 'gyur gyi yon bdag 'phags pa rigs gsum mgon
NK014(pha)014:2433: po rnam pa rgyal po'i tshul du bzung ba mnga'
NK014(pha)014:2434: bdag mes dbon rnam gsum yin pas /
NK014(pha)014:2435: phyis 'gyur ba rnams kyi yon bdag dang mi 'dra /
NK014(pha)014:2436: gnyis pa gang du bsgyur zhing gtan la phab pa'i gnas ni /
NK014(pha)014:2437: sngon sprul pa'i gtsug lag khang bsam yas sogs chos 'khor stod smad du yin pas /
NK014(pha)014:2438: da lta'i dgon phag phug tu bsgyur ba 'di dang mi 'dra /
NK014(pha)014:2439: gsum pa sgyur byed lo ts+aa ba'i khyad par ni /
NK014(pha)014:2440: sngon gyi lo ts+aa ba sgra sgyur bee ro tsa na dang ska cog zhang gsum /
NK014(pha)014:2441: rma gnyags sogs sprul pa'i lo ts+wa bas bsgyur ba'i chos yin /
NK014(pha)014:2442: da lta'i lo ts+aa ba dbyar mang yul du bsdad /
NK014(pha)014:2443: dgun rgya bal du yug re phyin nas bsgyur ba dang mi 'dra /
NK014(pha)014:2444: bzhi pa pan+di ta'i khyad par ni /
NK014(pha)014:2445: sngon gyi pan+di ta mkhan po zhi ba 'tsho dang /
NK014(pha)014:2447: slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas dang /
NK014(pha)014:2448: pan chen bi ma la mi tra sogs sangs rgyas dang /
NK014(pha)014:2449: sa chen po la bzhugs pa'i byang 'phags rnams kyis spyan drangs pa'i chos yin /
NK014(pha)014:2450: da lta'i gser tshol du 'khyams pa'i pan+di ta dang mi 'dra /
NK014(pha)014:2451: lnga pa zhu rten me tog gi khyad par ni /
NK014(pha)014:2452: gser sha ba'i blud bu bkang ba dang /
NK014(pha)014:2453: bres gzhal nas phul te zhus pa'i chos yin /
NK014(pha)014:2454: da lta mchan nas gser zho re re gnyis gnyis bton nas zhus pa dang mi 'dra /
NK014(pha)014:2455: drug pa chos kyi khyad par ni /
NK014(pha)014:2456: sngon 'phags yul du sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa gra ma nyams pa'i dus su bsgyur ba ma zad /
NK014(pha)014:2457: 'phags yul na med pa'i rgyud dbang thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK014(pha)014:2460: mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis bzung ste dag pa'i zhing na bzhugs pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2461: dzam bu gling gi cha shas sing+ga la dang /
NK014(pha)014:2462: nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul sogs nas slob dpon
NK014(pha)014:2463: chen po pad+ma dang bi ma la sogs kyis rdzu
NK014(pha)014:2464: 'phrul gyi bkod pas blangs nas bsgyur bas rgya gar
NK014(pha)014:2465: du pan grub yongs la ma grags pa mang po
NK014(pha)014:2466: zhig kyang bod kyi bsod nams kyi skal bar byon
NK014(pha)014:2467: / 'gyur kyang sngon gyi lo ts+aa ba rnams sprul
NK014(pha)014:2468: pa'i sku yin pas don ji lta ba bzhin du
NK014(pha)014:2469: gtan la phebs pas go sla zhing dbyings 'jal ba
NK014(pha)014:2470: / la rlabs che / phyis kyi lo ts+aa ba
NK014(pha)014:2471: rnams kyis don bsgyur ma nus par rgya dpe'i go
NK014(pha)014:2472: rim ltar sgra 'gyur byas pas tshig sgrim la go
NK014(pha)014:2473: / la rlabs che / dka' / dbyings 'jal ba
NK014(pha)014:2474: la rlabs chung ba ltar snang bas mi 'dra ba
NK014(pha)014:2475: / la rlabs che / dka' / yin no //
NK014(pha)014:2476: khyad par de ldan gyi gsang sngags rnying ma de
NK014(pha)014:2477: / la rlabs che / dka' / yin no // la'ang / zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' ma /
NK014(pha)014:2478: rjes su gnang ba'i gter ma /
NK014(pha)014:2479: byin gyis brlabs pa'i dag snang ma ste /
NK014(pha)014:2480: brgyud pa'i bka' srol gsum du gnas shing /
NK014(pha)014:2481: de thams cad kyi brjod bya rjod byed spyi'i lus kyis phye na /
NK014(pha)014:2483: sgrub sde gnyis su 'dus pa las /
NK014(pha)014:2484: de'i dang po rgyud sde la'ang gsum ste /
NK014(pha)014:2487: man ngag a ti yo ga'o //
NK014(pha)014:2488: de gsum gyi khyad par la /
NK014(pha)014:2489: lha rje zur chung ba'i zhal nas /
NK014(pha)014:2490: rig pa'i cho 'phrul du snang ba ma h+aa /
NK014(pha)014:2491: rang rig pa'i rtsal du snang ba a nu /
NK014(pha)014:2492: rig par snang ba a ti'o //
NK014(pha)014:2493: zhes gsungs pa'i dgongs pa ni /
NK014(pha)014:2494: chos thams cad sems nyid snang stong dbyer med kyi cho 'phrul du rtogs pas /
NK014(pha)014:2495: thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa dang spyod pa la gtso bor brten pa rgyud ma h+aa yo ga /
NK014(pha)014:2496: chos thams cad sems nyid dbyings ye gnyis su med pa'i rtsal du rtogs pas /
NK014(pha)014:2497: shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa dang ting nge 'dzin gtso bor brten pa lung a nu yo ga /
NK014(pha)014:2498: chos thams cad ye nas skye 'gags med pa'i rang byung gi ye shes rang snang bar rtogs pas /
NK014(pha)014:2499: ye thog tu grol bar byed pa'i thabs spangs blang re dogs dang bral ba ste /
NK014(pha)014:2500: lta ba la gtso bor brten pa rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'o //
NK014(pha)014:2503: de yang ma h+aa yo ga zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na rnal 'byor chen po ste /
NK014(pha)014:2504: gnyis med kyi don la blo 'byor bas yo ga
NK014(pha)014:2505: phyi pa las ches khyad par du 'phags pa'i phyir
NK014(pha)014:2507: bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug gi sgo nas 'khor 'das mnyam
NK014(pha)014:2508: pa nyid kyi don la rtogs goms kyis sbyor bas
NK014(pha)014:2509: grol ba thob pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK014(pha)014:2510: 'di ni theg pa 'og ma rnams kun rdzob rdzas
NK014(pha)014:2511: yod dang brtags yod du bzung nas bzang ngan blang
NK014(pha)014:2512: dor du lta ba las 'phags te /
NK014(pha)014:2513: 'dir chos rnams la mi gnyis pa'i bsam spyod dang ldan pas /
NK014(pha)014:2514: 'bras bu'i ngo bo snang stong zung 'jug gi chos skur rtogs par byas nas /
NK014(pha)014:2515: de dang rjes su mthun pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis goms par byed pa'i phyir te /
NK014(pha)014:2516: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK014(pha)014:2517: thabs kyi theg pa chen por ni //
NK014(pha)014:2518: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK014(pha)014:2519: kun rdzob tu'ang dbyer med de //
NK014(pha)014:2520: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK014(pha)014:2522: de ji ltar nyams su len pa'i khyad par yang /
NK014(pha)014:2524: rnal 'byor bla ma yi ni mtshan //
NK014(pha)014:2525: gsang ba yi ni dbang rgyal bshad //
NK014(pha)014:2526: shes rab ye shes bla na med //
NK014(pha)014:2527: bzhi pa de yang de bzhin no //
NK014(pha)014:2529: sgyu 'phrul rtsa rgyud phyi ma las /
NK014(pha)014:2530: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang //
NK014(pha)014:2531: de ma thag pa bzhi pa ste //
NK014(pha)014:2532: zhes bum dbang gi steng du /
NK014(pha)014:2533: thun mong ma yin pa mchog dbang gong ma gsum
NK014(pha)014:2534: bsnan nas dbang bzhi bskur bas snod rung du byas
NK014(pha)014:2535: la / lam bskyed rim ma dag pa'i snang ba
NK014(pha)014:2536: dbyings su sbyangs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lor bsgom
NK014(pha)014:2537: la / zhing / dbang dang bskyed rim gnyis ka la /
NK014(pha)014:2538: yar 'bras bu'i bzhugs tshul dang rnam pa mthun pa'i lam du byed tshul dang /
NK014(pha)014:2539: mar 'khor ba dang rnam pa mthun pa'i dri ma sbyong tshul te /
NK014(pha)014:2544: thun mtshams su yang snang ba thams cad lhar bsgom /
NK014(pha)014:2545: rdzogs rim rdo rje'i lus la gnad du bsnun pa'i thabs kyis /
NK014(pha)014:2548: rlung rnams dbu mar thim pas mngon du gyur pa'i bde stong zung 'jug sgrub /
NK014(pha)014:2549: spyod pa rnam pa gsum gyi nye rgyus 'bras bu la sbyor bar bzhed /
NK014(pha)014:2550: de yang bsam pa'i stobs che ba gcig gis 'bad pas bsgoms na /
NK014(pha)014:2551: tshe lo brgya pa'i tshe gang gcig gi yun la
NK014(pha)014:2552: lam gzhan la ma ltos par 'tshang rgya nus par
NK014(pha)014:2553: gsungs / de lta bu'i ma h+aa yo ga de
NK014(pha)014:2554: la'ang bskyed rim thabs kyi cha sogs rang rang gi
NK014(pha)014:2556: yang me tog dang mig dar dgos pa'i rigs la man+dala gyi mjug tu /
NK014(pha)014:2557: 'o de ltar man+dala 'bul ba'i rim pa de song nas /
NK014(pha)014:2558: slar yang khyed cag rnams sngon chad ming 'di zhes bya ba'i dkyil 'khor du ma zhugs pa'am /
NK014(pha)014:2559: zhugs su zin kyang skabs 'dir yang bskyar nas 'jug
NK014(pha)014:2560: dgos pas da lta'i dkyil 'khor gsar pa 'di nyid
NK014(pha)014:2561: mthong ba la sgrib par byed pa ma rig pa'i
NK014(pha)014:2562: ling thog mtshon phyir ras yug dmar po sogs re
NK014(pha)014:2563: res mig bkab pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK014(pha)014:2565: dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang mjal ba'i tshe phyag stong
NK014(pha)014:2566: par mjal du mi rung bas phyag rten gyi slad
NK014(pha)014:2567: du me tog u dum wa ra la sogs pa'i
NK014(pha)014:2568: chun po kha dog lnga ldan re phyag tu thogs
NK014(pha)014:2570: +aahmh'u zhes pa'am yang na sngags snga mas gtad kyang rung ngo //
NK014(pha)014:2571: de ltar me tog gtad nas /
NK014(pha)014:2573: slar yang snyim pa me tog dang bcas te thal
NK014(pha)014:2574: mo sbyar nas gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rjes zlos
NK014(pha)014:2578: slar yang lha gang dang smon lam gyis 'brel pa
NK014(pha)014:2579: brtag pa'i don du me tog dor ba la tshig
NK014(pha)014:2583: slar yang slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas 'od zer
NK014(pha)014:2584: gser gyi thur ma 'dra ba 'phros pas khyed rang
NK014(pha)014:2585: rnams kyi ma rig pa'i ling thog mig dar dang
NK014(pha)014:2586: lhan cig bsal nas dag pa ye shes kyi spyan
NK014(pha)014:2587: dang ldan par gyur pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK014(pha)014:2589: 'jug pa rdzogs nas dbang dngos gzhi'i mgor sleb pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:2590: 'o de dag gis 'jug pa'i chos rnams legs par
NK014(pha)014:2591: song nas slar yang dbang dngos gzhi zhu ba'i yon
NK014(pha)014:2593: ces pa lta bu skabs thob shes pas mtshams sbyor ci rigs pa sbyar bar bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:2594: de dag ni dbang thams cad kyi sngon 'gro sbyor ba'i skabs kyi rgyug byang ngo //
NK014(pha)014:2595: de nas rjes kyi bya ba ni /
NK014(pha)014:2596: sta gon gyi mjug tu bkra shis rgya cher brjod pas mtha' brgyan par bya ste /
NK014(pha)014:2598: 'o de dag gis sta gon gyi chos rnams legs
NK014(pha)014:2599: par grub ste slar yang phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras
NK014(pha)014:2600: dang slob mar bcas pa thams cad mdun gyi nam
NK014(pha)014:2601: mkhar byon te / phyag nas me tog gi sil
NK014(pha)014:2602: ma kun tu 'thor zhing zhal nas bkra shis pa'i
NK014(pha)014:2603: glu dbyangs phyogs bcur sgrogs pa'i mos pa mdzod cig
NK014(pha)014:2604: mkhar byon te / / ye d+har+m+aa te tu pra
NK014(pha)014:2605: b+ha w+aa he tun+te sh+aan+ta th+aa ga to h+ya wa
NK014(pha)014:2606: mkhar byon te / / data / te sh+aany+tsa yo
NK014(pha)014:2607: ni ro d+ha e wam b+aa d+ai ma h+aa sh+ra
NK014(pha)014:2609: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK014(pha)014:2611: mtho ris dag na rin chen mchog yod pa //
NK014(pha)014:2612: de bzhin gshegs pa lha yi lhar gyur pa //
NK014(pha)014:2613: mi yi mchog dang 'dir ni mtshungs pa med //
NK014(pha)014:2614: de bas 'di ni rin chen mchog tu gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2615: bden pa de yis 'dir ni dge bar shog /
NK014(pha)014:2616: zad pa chags bral bdud rtsi 'dus ma byas //
NK014(pha)014:2617: shes pas sh+aakya thub des rab tu phye //
NK014(pha)014:2618: bdud rtsi zhi ba 'dus byas ma yin pa //
NK014(pha)014:2619: chos de dang ni mtshungs pa gang yang med //
NK014(pha)014:2620: de bas 'di ni rin chen mchog tu gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2621: bden pa de yis 'dir ni dge bar shog /
NK014(pha)014:2622: mchog tu gang 'dod tshul bzhin rab bstan pa //
NK014(pha)014:2623: ston pa'i rnal 'byor bla med rtag sgrub pa //
NK014(pha)014:2624: rdo rje lta bu'i mig gnyis lam mthong ba //
NK014(pha)014:2625: ting 'dzin de dang mnyam pa yod ma yin //
NK014(pha)014:2626: de bas 'di ni rin chen mchog tu gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2627: bden pa de yis 'dir ni dge bar shog /
NK014(pha)014:2628: gang zag chen po brgyad po rab basngagasa shing //
NK014(pha)014:2629: gang zag zung bzhir brjod pa de dag ni //
NK014(pha)014:2630: drang srong chen po gang zag mtshungs med pa //
NK014(pha)014:2631: bde bar gshegs pas sbyiin pa'i gnas zhes gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2632: de la sbyin na 'bras bu cher 'gyur te //
NK014(pha)014:2633: zhing rab gshin la sa bon btab pa bzhin //
NK014(pha)014:2634: 'di ni dge 'dun rin chen mchog tu gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2635: bden pa de yis 'dir ni dge bar shog /
NK014(pha)014:2636: gang dag bstan pa'i yid kyis rab brtson zhing //
NK014(pha)014:2637: goo ta ma yi bstan la 'jug byed pa //
NK014(pha)014:2638: de dag thob nas bdud rtsi 'jug thob ste //
NK014(pha)014:2639: mun pa bsal nas mya ngan 'das thob pa //
NK014(pha)014:2640: de bas dge 'dun rin chen mchog tu gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2641: bden pa de yis 'dir ni dge bar shog /
NK014(pha)014:2642: lta ba 'di la sbyar ma thag tu ni //
NK014(pha)014:2643: 'jig tshogs lta dang tshul khrims brtul zhugs dang //
NK014(pha)014:2644: the tshom dang ni nyon mongs gsum po dag /
NK014(pha)014:2645: cig char spangs te 'phags pa'i bden mthong ba //
NK014(pha)014:2646: des na dge 'dun rin chen mchog tu gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2647: bden pa de yis 'dir ni dge bar shog /
NK014(pha)014:2648: lus sam ngag gam 'on te yid kyi kyang //
NK014(pha)014:2649: sdig pa rnam gsum nam yang mi byed cing //
NK014(pha)014:2650: glo bur byas na'ang 'chab par mi byed la //
NK014(pha)014:2651: de ltar de dag lta bas 'dzin mi byed //
NK014(pha)014:2652: de bas dge 'dun rin chen mchog tu gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2653: bden pa de yis 'dir ni dge bar shog /
NK014(pha)014:2654: ji ltar dbang po'i sdong po sar btsugs pa //
NK014(pha)014:2655: phyogs bzhi'i rlung rnams kyis ni mi g.yo ltar //
NK014(pha)014:2656: 'phags pa'i lam gyi dam pa mthong ba yi //
NK014(pha)014:2657: gang zag 'phags pa'i dge 'dun de bzhin no //
NK014(pha)014:2658: des na dge 'dun rin chen mchog tu gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2659: bden pa de yis 'dir ni dge bar shog /
NK014(pha)014:2660: shes rab zab mos shin tu bstan pa yi //
NK014(pha)014:2661: 'phags pa'i bden pa su dag rnam sgom zhing //
NK014(pha)014:2662: lus kyang sbyin par yid la byas pa ni //
NK014(pha)014:2663: de dag 'jigs pa brgyad dang 'phrad mi 'gyur //
NK014(pha)014:2664: des na dge 'dun rin chen mchog tu gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2665: bden pa de yis 'dir ni dge bar shog /
NK014(pha)014:2666: ji ltar me ni rlung gis rab gtor ba //
NK014(pha)014:2667: lag tu blangs te bgrang du med pa nyid //
NK014(pha)014:2668: de ltar kun tu sbyar ba rab btang ba //
NK014(pha)014:2669: sangs rgyas sras rnams bstan du med par 'gro //
NK014(pha)014:2670: des na dge 'dun rin chen mchog tu gsungs //
NK014(pha)014:2671: bden pa de yis 'dir ni dge bar shog /
NK014(pha)014:2672: sems can gang dag 'gro dang mi 'gro ba //
NK014(pha)014:2673: de dag thams cad 'dir ni bde gyur cig /
NK014(pha)014:2674: ston mchog lha dang mis ni mchod 'os pa //
NK014(pha)014:2675: sangs rgyas phyag 'tshal deng 'dir dge bar shog /
NK014(pha)014:2676: sems can gang dag 'gro dang mi 'gro ba //
NK014(pha)014:2677: de dag thams cad 'dir ni bde gyur cig /
NK014(pha)014:2678: zhi ba chags bral lha mis mchod 'os pa //
NK014(pha)014:2679: chos la phyag 'tshal deng 'dir dge bar shog /
NK014(pha)014:2680: sems can gang dag 'gro dang mi 'gro ba //
NK014(pha)014:2681: de dag thams cad 'dir ni bde gyur cig /
NK014(pha)014:2682: tshogs kyi dam pa lha mis mchod 'os pa //
NK014(pha)014:2683: dge 'dun phyag 'tshal deng 'dir dge bar shog /

NK014(pha)014:2959: 'jig rten gsum mgon 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i sku //
NK014(pha)014:2960: bde gshegs sku yi bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK014(pha)014:2961: bkra shis des ni deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK014(pha)014:2962: bcom ldan dung mdog ri yi rgyal po 'dra //
NK014(pha)014:2963: 'jig rten gsum mgon spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang //
NK014(pha)014:2964: bde gshegs gsung gi bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK014(pha)014:2965: bkra shis des ni deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK014(pha)014:2966: bcom ldan ljang ser ri yi rgyal po 'dra //
NK014(pha)014:2967: 'jig rten gsum mgon phyag na rdo rje ste //
NK014(pha)014:2968: bde gshegs thugs kyi bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK014(pha)014:2969: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK014(pha)014:2971: rgya mtsho lta bur brgal dka' 'khor ba'i 'dam las brgal //
NK014(pha)014:2972: bsod nams ye shes tshogs gnyis bsags dka' ma lus rdzogs //
NK014(pha)014:2973: 'gro ba kun gyi gnyen gcig gyur pa de bzhin gshegs //
NK014(pha)014:2974: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK014(pha)014:2975: rang don spangs shing gzhan don rtag tu lhur len cing //
NK014(pha)014:2976: 'dod pa'i 'dod yon lnga la lta ba rgyangs bsrings te //
NK014(pha)014:2977: dad dang brtson 'grus lhur len grogs mchog byang chub sems //
NK014(pha)014:2978: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK014(pha)014:2979: skye 'gags med cing rtog pa'i 'ching byed mtha' dag spangs //
NK014(pha)014:2980: ma rig mun pa 'joms byed stong nyid sgron ma'i mchog /
NK014(pha)014:2981: dmigs pa sna tshogs spangs pa la lam gyi bde sgrub chos //
NK014(pha)014:2982: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK014(pha)014:2984: yon tan rgyas pa'i rtags su sku mdog gser 'dra ba //
NK014(pha)014:2985: shes rab rtags su ral gri po ti phyag na bsnams //
NK014(pha)014:2986: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK014(pha)014:2987: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK014(pha)014:2988: thugs rje'i rtags su sku mdog zla ba'i 'od chags pa //
NK014(pha)014:2989: skyon gyis ma gos phyag mtshan phyag na pad+ma bsnams //
NK014(pha)014:2990: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs kyi bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK014(pha)014:2991: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK014(pha)014:2992: chos nyid mi 'gyur rtags su sku mdog mthing nag sngo //
NK014(pha)014:2993: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med phyag na rdo rje bsnams //
NK014(pha)014:2994: 'phags pa phyag na rdo rje'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK014(pha)014:2995: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK014(pha)014:2997: phun sum tshogs pa mnga' ba gser gyi ri bo 'dra //
NK014(pha)014:2998: 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon po dri ma gsum spangs pa //
NK014(pha)014:2999: sangs rgyas pad+ma rgyas pa'i 'dab 'dra'i spyan mnga' ba //
NK014(pha)014:3000: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed dang po'o //
NK014(pha)014:3001: de yis nye bar bstan pa'i mchog rab mi g.yo ba //
NK014(pha)014:3002: 'jig rten gsum na grags shing lha dang mis mchod pa //
NK014(pha)014:3003: chos kyi dam pa skye rgu rnams la zhi byed pa //
NK014(pha)014:3004: de ni 'jig rten dge ba'i bkra shis gnyis pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:3005: dge 'dun dam pa'i chos ldan thob pa'i bkra shis phyug /
NK014(pha)014:3006: mi dang lha dang lha ma yin gyis mchod pa'i gnas //
NK014(pha)014:3007: tshogs kyi mchog rab ngo tsha shes dang dpal gyi gzhi //
NK014(pha)014:3008: de ni 'jig rten dge ba'i bkra shis gsum pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:3009: sems can kun la phan phyir byang chub mnga' ba po //
NK014(pha)014:3010: don rnams thams cad 'grub par brtul ba yongs ldan pa //
NK014(pha)014:3011: tshogs kyi lam dgyes thub pa'i bkra shis gang byung ba //
NK014(pha)014:3012: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3013: 'gro la phan phyir de bzhin gshegs pa dga' ldan lha'i //
NK014(pha)014:3014: gzhal med khang gi snying po nas ni 'dir gshegs te //
NK014(pha)014:3015: dbang bcas lha yis bskor ba'i bkra shis gang byung ba //
NK014(pha)014:3016: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3017: lo ma me tog 'od 'bar nyams dga' lum+bi'i tshal //
NK014(pha)014:3018: lha mang dag gis bsten par mgon po bltams pa na //
NK014(pha)014:3019: srid pa mthar phyin pa yi bkra shis gang byung ba //
NK014(pha)014:3020: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3021: grong khyer ser skya'i gnas nas rgyal po'i pho brang du //
NK014(pha)014:3022: lhums nas bltams pa ston pa bde gshegs zas gtsang sras //
NK014(pha)014:3023: myur bskrun bdud rtsi'i chus gtor ba yi bkra shis gang //
NK014(pha)014:3024: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3025: grong khyer dam pa ser skya'i gnas zhes bya bar ni //
NK014(pha)014:3026: rmad du grags pa che ba'i lha yis mngon bstod pa //
NK014(pha)014:3027: bsam yas dge bsgrubs bsod nams phung po'i bkra shis gang //
NK014(pha)014:3028: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3029: dgyes shing nam phyed grong khyer mchog nas mngon byung ste //
NK014(pha)014:3030: dka' thub tshal du mngon par gshegs shing tshangs la sogs //
NK014(pha)014:3031: lha yi tshogs kyis yongs su bskor ba'i bkra shis gang //
NK014(pha)014:3032: bkra shis de ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3033: rab tu 'od 'bar gser dang 'dra ba'i sku mnga' zhing //
NK014(pha)014:3034: bee d+aur+ya ltar sngo ba'i rtsa bting steng bzhugs te //
NK014(pha)014:3035: skyil mo krung bcas mi g.yo mchog gi bkra shis gang //
NK014(pha)014:3036: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3037: chu bo'i 'gram na r+ts+wa sha'i phreng gis yongs bskor ba //
NK014(pha)014:3038: shin tu rmad du byung ba'i srid pa sel mdzad pa //
NK014(pha)014:3039: klu yis rgyal pos phyag byas pa yi bkra shis gang //
NK014(pha)014:3040: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3041: shing rgyal drung gshegs byams pa'i stobs kyis bdud kyi phyogs //
NK014(pha)014:3042: mang po btul te sa steng dang ni nam mkha' la //
NK014(pha)014:3043: bcom ldan bkra shis rnam pa sna tshogs gang byung ba //
NK014(pha)014:3044: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3045: sdug bsngal mtha' dag gzhig phyir rdo rje'i gdan bzhugs te //
NK014(pha)014:3046: nam gyi tho rangs bdud bzhi dgra bo rnams btul ba //
NK014(pha)014:3047: ston pa bde bar gshegs pa'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK014(pha)014:3048: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3049: grong khyer wa ra n+aa sir drang srong mchog bzhugs nas //
NK014(pha)014:3050: chos kyi 'khor lo mchog brtan pa yi bkra shis gang //
NK014(pha)014:3051: lha yul deng 'dir shin tu rmad du byung gyur pa //
NK014(pha)014:3052: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3053: bkra shis gang zhig phan byed dam pa dag byed pa //
NK014(pha)014:3054: bsod nams bya byed 'phags pa'i skye bos mngon bstod pa //
NK014(pha)014:3055: bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa'i seng ges gang gsungs pa //
NK014(pha)014:3056: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3057: mu stegs byed pa kun gyi nga rgyal gzhom pa dang //
NK014(pha)014:3058: 'gro la bde ba bskyed phyir cho 'phrul dag pa dag /
NK014(pha)014:3059: nye bar ston pa rgyal ba'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK014(pha)014:3060: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3061: 'gro la phan phyir mtho ris nas ni 'dir gshegs te //
NK014(pha)014:3062: tshangs pa la sogs lha tshogs lag na rnga yab gdugs //
NK014(pha)014:3063: sna tshogs thogs pas yongs su bskor ba'i bkra shis gang //
NK014(pha)014:3064: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3065: de bzhin gshegs pa zhi ba mchog tu nyer gshegs pa //
NK014(pha)014:3066: man+d+ha ra ba'i me tog mang pos mngon mchod pa //
NK014(pha)014:3067: lha mchog rnams kyis mngon par bstod pa'i bkra shis gang //
NK014(pha)014:3068: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3069: lha dang klu dang mi yi dbang pos phyag byas pa //
NK014(pha)014:3070: mkha' lding gnod sbyin dri za'i dbang pos mchod gyur pa //
NK014(pha)014:3071: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu ldan pa'i bkra shis gang //
NK014(pha)014:3072: bkra shis des ni skye rgu rnams la zhi byed shog /
NK014(pha)014:3074: che ba'i che mchog ston mchog bla na med //
NK014(pha)014:3075: chos rje nyi ma rgyal ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK014(pha)014:3076: bdud dang bgegs rigs gnod pa'i dgra zhi ste //
NK014(pha)014:3077: rtag tu dpal gnas nyin mtshan bkra shis shog /
NK014(pha)014:3078: chos nyid bden pa'i chos mchog bla na med //
NK014(pha)014:3079: dam chos bdud rtsi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK014(pha)014:3080: nyes pa'i skyon bral dge tshogs rnam 'phel ba //
NK014(pha)014:3081: rtag tu dpal gnas nyin mtshan bkra shis shog /
NK014(pha)014:3082: dge 'dun yon tan rin chen dpal 'bar ba //
NK014(pha)014:3083: rgyal sras phan mdzad bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK014(pha)014:3084: nyon mongs sdug bsngal gdung ba'i dgra zhi ste //
NK014(pha)014:3085: rtag tu dpal gnas nyin mtshan bkra shis shog /
NK014(pha)014:3086: tshangs dang lha dbang srung ma'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK014(pha)014:3087: phan mdzad lha yi bkra shis gnas gyur te //
NK014(pha)014:3088: bde legs bsam pa yid bzhin 'grub pa dang //
NK014(pha)014:3089: tshe ring nad med bde skyid ldan par shog /
NK014(pha)014:3090: dkon mchog gsum gyi bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa /
NK014(pha)014:3091: bcom ldan 'das kyis khyim bdag des pa la gsungs pa rdzogs so //
NK014(pha)014:3092: rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang /
NK014(pha)014:3093: zhu chen gyi lo ts+aa ba ban+de ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa'o //
NK014(pha)014:3094: zhes pa rnams las gang rung re blangs nas brjod par bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:3095: dngos gzhi'i nyin dbang rdzogs pa dang /
NK014(pha)014:3096: 'o de ltar dbang bskur legs par thob pa de la /
NK014(pha)014:3097: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sogs sta gon gyi skabs ltar
NK014(pha)014:3098: brjod pa'i bkra shis mthar dam tshig gi rnam dbye
NK014(pha)014:3100: 'o de ltar rtsa ba dang yan lag gis bsdus
NK014(pha)014:3101: pa'i dam tshig gi rim pa rnams rdo rje slob
NK014(pha)014:3102: dpon gyi bka' ji ltar stsal ba bzhin du bsrung
NK014(pha)014:3103: bar bagyi'o snyam pas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK014(pha)014:3104: gtso bos ji ltar bka' stsal ba //
NK014(pha)014:3105: de dag thams cad bdag gis bgyi //
NK014(pha)014:3107: de ltar dbang legs par thob pa'i bka' drin gtang rag gi yon du man+dala phul /
NK014(pha)014:3109: slar yang rang rang rnams kyi lus longs spyod dus
NK014(pha)014:3110: gsum du bsags pa'i dge tshogs rgya mtsho dang bcas
NK014(pha)014:3111: pa thams cad gcig tu bsdoms nas 'khor los sgyur
NK014(pha)014:3112: ba'i rgyal srid kyi 'byor pa ltar sprul te 'bul
NK014(pha)014:3113: na cha shas nas longs spyod du gsol snyam pas
NK014(pha)014:3115: deng nas brtsams te bdag bran du //
NK014(pha)014:3116: khyed la bdag ni 'bul lags na //
NK014(pha)014:3117: khyed kyis slob mar gzung ba dang //
NK014(pha)014:3118: cha shas kyang ni spyad du gsol //
NK014(pha)014:3120: de ltar dbang legs par thob pa'i dge rtsa sems
NK014(pha)014:3121: can thams cad kyi don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK014(pha)014:3122: kyi go 'phang rin po che mngon du 'thob pa'i
NK014(pha)014:3123: ched du yongs su bsngo ba'i thugs 'dun gnang 'tshal
NK014(pha)014:3124: / 'jam dpal dpa' bos ji ltar mkhyen pa dang //
NK014(pha)014:3126: bsod nams 'di yis thams cad gzigs pa nyid //
NK014(pha)014:3127: ces sogs bsngo smon gyis mtha' brgyan par bya'o //
NK014(pha)014:3128: zhes pa 'di yang rnal 'byor ma ak+sha ra sh+r+ai
NK014(pha)014:3129: d+ai pam gyis mdzad pa'i zhi khro na raka dong
NK014(pha)014:3130: sprugs kyi dbang gi mtshams sbyor dang /
NK014(pha)014:3131: lo chen rin po che d+harma sh+r+ai'i dbang gi 'khyogs
NK014(pha)014:3132: mtshams kyi bshad pa dag las khol du bton nas
NK014(pha)014:3133: 'khrugs bsdebs kyi rim pas gtan la phab pa ste
NK014(pha)014:3134: / btsun pa gzhan phan pas snga 'gyur bka' ma'i
NK014(pha)014:3135: dbang chog rnams kyi yan lag tu legs par sbyar
